%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67347201.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67347201.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWhy%20Help%20Virat%20When%20He%20Had%20A%20Cramp%3F%26quot%3B%3A%20Ex-Australia%20Star%20Questions%20Kiwis%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECricket%20fraternity%20the%20world%20over%20might%20be%20cherishing%20Virat%20Kohli's%20record-setting%2050th%20ODI%20century%20but%20former%20Australian%20pacer%20Simon%20O'Donnell%20has%20flayed%20New%20Zealand's%20gesture%20of%20helping%20the%20batting%20great%20when%20he%20was%20suffering%20from%20cramps%20during%20the%20World%20Cup%20semifinal.%20Kohli%2C%2035%2C%20was%20seen%20struggling%20with%20cramps%20during%20his%20113-ball%20117%2C%20which%20powered%20India%20into%20the%20World%20Cup%20final%20at%20the%20Wankhede%20Stadium%20here%20on%20Wednesday.%20A%20few%20New%20Zealand%20players%20opted%20to%20assist%20the%20star%20India%20batter%20while%20he%20was%20struggling%20with%20cramps%2C%20and%20O'Donnell%20said%20he%20had%20a%20%26quot%3Bproblem%26quot%3B%20with%20that%20gesture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKohli's%20century%20and%20pacer%20Mohammed%20Shami's%20seven-wicket%20haul%20helped%20India%20maul%20the%20Blackcaps%20by%2070%20runs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20a%20problem%20a%20couple%20of%20times%20last%20night.%20Virat%20Kohli%20gets%20cramp%2C%20they're%20(India)%20heading%20for%20400%20(runs)%20and%20(New%20Zealand)%20blokes%20go%20over%20and%20help%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20O'Donnell%2C%20who%20played%2087%20ODIs%20for%20Australia%20primarily%20as%20a%20pace%20bowler%2C%20said%20on%20Sen%20Radio.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20would%20you%20go%20and%20help%20Virat%20Kohli%20when%20he%20had%20a%20cramp%3F%20When%20they're%20heading%20for%20400.%20In%20a%20World%20Cup%20semifinal.%20Spirit%20of%20the%20game%20is%20playing%20within%20the%20laws.%20Vi