by%20food%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bmedical%20supplies%2C%26quot%3B%20while%20health%20officials%20talked%20of%20terrified%20staff%20and%20patients%20as%20troops%20moved%20through%20the%20buildings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20encircling%20Al%20Shifa%20for%20days%2C%20Israel%20faced%20pressure%20to%20prove%20its%20claim%20that%20Hamas%20had%20turned%20the%20hospital%20into%20a%20command%20center%20and%20used%20patients%2C%20staff%2C%20and%20civilians%20sheltering%20there%20to%20provide%20cover%20for%20its%20militants.%20The%20allegation%20is%20part%20of%20Israel's%20broader%20accusation%20that%20Hamas%20uses%20Palestinians%20as%20human%20shields.%20Israel%20released%20video%20late%20Wednesday%20of%20weapons%20it%20said%20it%20found%20in%20one%20building%2C%20but%20so%20far%20its%20search%20showed%20no%20signs%20of%20tunnels%20or%20a%20sophisticated%20command%20center.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHamas%20and%20Gaza%20health%20officials%20deny%20militants%20operate%20in%20Al%20Shifa%20%E2%80%94%20a%20hospital%20that%20employs%20some%201%2C500%20people%20and%20has%20more%20than%20500%20beds%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Palestinian%20news%20agency.%20Palestinians%20and%20rights%20groups%20say%20Israel%20has%20recklessly%20endangered%20civilians%20as%20it%20seeks%20to%20eradicate%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Israel%20tightens%20its%20hold%20on%20northern%20Gaza%2C%20leaders%20have%20talked%20of%20expanding%20the%20ground%20operation%20into%20the%20south%20to%20root%20out%20Hamas.%20Most%20of%20Gaza's%202.3%20million%20people%20have%20already%20crowded%20into%20the%20territory's%20south%2C%20where%20a%20worsening%20fuel%20shortage%20threatens%20to%20paralyze%20the%20delivery%20of%20humanitarian%20services%20and%20shut%20down%20mobile%20phone%20and%20internet%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20war%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%20erupted%20after%20the%20militant%20group%20killed%20some%201%2C200%20people%20and%20seized%20around%20240%20captives%20in%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fisrael-palestinians-gaza-hamas-rockets-airstrikes-tel-aviv-11fb98655c256d54ecb5329284fc37d2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20Oct.%207%20attack%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20shattered%20Israelis'%20sense%20of%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20airstrikes%20have%20since%20killed%20more%20than%2011%2C200%20people%2C%20two-thirds%20of%20them%20women%20and%20minors%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Palestinian%20Health%20Ministry%20in%20Ramallah%2C%20which%20coordinates%20with%20the%20ministry%20branch%20in%20Hamas-ruled%20Gaza.%20Another%202%2C700%20have%20been%20reported%20missing%2C%20with%20most%20believed%20to%20be%20buried%20under%20the%20rubble.%20The%20ministry's%20count%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fisrael-hamas-war-gaza-health-ministry-health-death-toll-59470820308b31f1faf73c703400b033%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edoes%20not%20differentiate%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0between%20civilian%20and%20militant%20deaths.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20forces%20launched%20their%20raid%20into%20the%20large%20Al%20Shifa%20compound%20around%202%20a.m.%20and%20remained%20on%20the%20grounds%20after%20nightfall%20Wednesday%2C%20with%20tanks%20stationed%20outside%20and%20snipers%20on%20nearby%20buildings%2C%20Munir%20al-Boursh%2C%20a%20senior%20official%20with%20Gaza's%20Health%20Ministry%20inside%20the%20hospital%2C%20told%20The%20Associated%20Press.%20It%20was%20not%20possible%20to%20independently%20assess%20the%20situation%20inside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAl-Boursh%20said%20that%20for%20hours%2C%20the%20troops%20ransacked%20the%20basement%20and%20other%20buildings%2C%20including%20those%20housing%20the%20emergency%20and%20surgery%20departments%2C%20and%20searched%20the%20grounds%20for%20tunnels.%20Troops%20questioned%20and%20face-screened%20patients%2C%20staff%2C%20and%20people%20sheltering%20in%20the%20facility%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20did%20not%20know%20if%20any%20were%20detained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPatients%2C%20women%2C%20and%20children%20are%20terrified%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20AP%20by%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeither%20the%20Palestinians%20nor%20the%20military%20reported%20any%20clashes%20inside%20the%20hospital.%20The%20military%20said%20its%20troops%20killed%20four%20militants%20outside%20the%20hospital%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20operation.%20Throughout%20days%20of%20fighting%20in%20the%20surrounding%20streets%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20report%20of%20militants%20firing%20from%20inside%20Al%20Shifa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20military%20said%20it%20was%20carrying%20out%20a%20%26quot%3Bprecise%20and%20targeted%20operation%20against%20Hamas%20in%20a%20specified%20area%20in%20the%20hospital%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20its%20soldiers%20were%20accompanied%20by%20medical%20teams%20bringing%20in%20incubators%20and%20other%20supplies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20added%20that%20forces%20were%20also%20searching%20for%20hostages.%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fisrael-hamas-war-hostages-gaza-ca1466cc052b08a642fff88280eb0b22%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20plight%20of%20the%20captives%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20include%20men%2C%20women%2C%20and%20children%2C%20has%20galvanized%20Israeli%20support%20for%20the%20war.%20Families%20and%20supporters%20of%20the%20hostages%20are%20holding%20a%20protest%20march%20from%20Tel%20Aviv%20to%20Jerusalem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20released%20by%20the%20military%20from%20inside%20Al%20Shifa%20showed%20three%20duffel%20bags%20it%20said%20it%20found%20hidden%20around%20an%20MRI%20lab%2C%20each%20containing%20an%20assault%20rifle%2C%20grenades%2C%20and%20Hamas%20uniforms%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20closet%20that%20contained%20a%20number%20of%20assault%20rifles%20without%20ammunition%20clips.%20A%20laptop%20was%20also%20discovered%20and%20taken%20for%20study.%20The%20AP%20could%20not%20independently%20verify%2