rl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20Biden%20and%20Xi%20Meet%2C%20What%E2%80%99s%20at%20Stake%20is%20Two%20Competing%20Visions%20for%20the%20World%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16090026%2FUntitled-design-6-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELeaving%20the%20Kremlin%20after%20his%20March%202023%20visit%2C%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20said%20to%20his%20Russian%20counterpart%20Vladimir%20Putin%20in%20full%20view%20of%20the%20media%2C%20%E2%80%98Right%20now%20there%20are%20changes%20%E2%80%93%20the%20likes%20of%20which%20we%20haven%E2%80%99t%20seen%20for%20100%20years%20%E2%80%93%20and%20we%20are%20the%20ones%20driving%20these%20changes%20together.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EXi%20was%20neither%20being%20pompous%20nor%20was%20he%20exaggerating.%20Together%20with%20Putin%2C%20Xi%20has%20unveiled%20an%20unparalleled%20and%20unbeatable%20vision%20of%20the%20new%20world%20order.%20Premised%20on%20the%20Chinese%20philosophy%20of%20win-win%20as%20against%20the%20traditional%20geopolitical%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emantra%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20zero-sum%2C%20Xi%20is%20looking%20at%20uniting%20the%20world%20through%20the%20Belt%20and%20Road%20Initiative%20(BRI)%2C%20a%20network%20of%20cooperative%20roads%2C%20seas%20lanes%2C%20and%20hard%20and%20soft%20cyberspace%20connectivity%20for%20seamless%20flow%20of%20trade%20and%20traffic.%20This%20vision%20is%20complimented%20by%20Putin%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98pivot%20to%20Asia%E2%80%99%20vision%20spelt%20out%20in%202012%20for%20Greater%20Eurasia%20(Eurasia%20plus%20ASEAN%2C%20India%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20the%20Arab%20world%2C%20and%20Iran)%20which%20seeks%20to%20create%20an%20economic%20cooperation%20zone%20from%20Eurasia%20(Russia%2C%20Belarus%2C%20Armenia%2C%20Kazakhstan%2C%20Kyrgyzstan)%20to%20the%20Asia-Pacific%2C%20thereby%20fusing%20the%20two%20visions%20together.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20the%20Global%20South%20(barring%20India)%20sees%20in%20these%20%E2%80%98once%20in%20a%20100-year%20changes%E2%80%99%20an%20opportunity%20to%20uplift%20its%20people%20and%20economy%20was%20evident%20from%20the%203%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Erd%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Belt%20and%20Road%20Forum%20(BRF)%20to%20mark%20the%2010%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Anniversary%20of%20the%20BRI%20held%20in%20Beijing%20on%20October%2017%20and%2018.%20Nearly%20150%20Global%20South%20nations%20had%20representation%20at%20the%20Forum%20with%2023%20heads%20of%20the%20state%20participating%20in%20it.%20Of%20course%2C%20Putin%20was%20the%20guest%20of%20honour.%20And%20India%20was%20not%20invited%20to%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-and-china-are-trapped-in-a-conflict-of-their-own-making%5C%22%3EIndia%20and%20China%20are%20Trapped%20in%20a%20Conflict%20of%20Their%20Own%20Making%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20two%20global%20powers%2C%20China%20and%20Russia%2C%20are%20forging%20a%20path%20towards%20a%20new%20cooperative%20world%2C%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20world%2C%20the%20third%20global%20power%2C%20the%20United%20States%2C%20still%20tied%20to%20old%20ideas%20of%20competition%2C%20is%20floundering%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20vision%20for%20the%20new%20world.%20This%20confusion%20was%20summed%20up%20by%20US%20national%20security%20advisor%2C%20Jake%20Sullivan%20recently.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foreignaffairs.com%2Fauthors%2Fjake-sullivan%5C%22%3EIn%20his%20essay%20in%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foreignaffairs.com%2Fauthors%2Fjake-sullivan%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EForeign%20Affairs%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foreignaffairs.com%2Fauthors%2Fjake-sullivan%5C%22%3E%20magazine%3C%2Fa%3E%20(November%2FDecember%202023)%2C%20he%20wrote%20that%20America%20must%20adjust%20to%20%E2%80%98the%20main%20challenge%20it%20faces%3A%20competition%20(with%20China)%20in%20an%20age%20of%20interdependence.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20world%20is%20interdependent%2C%20the%20natural%20thing%20should%20be%20cooperation%20and%20not%20competition.%20And%20since%20there%20is%20a%20thin%20line%20between%20competition%20and%20conflict%2C%20in%20his%20State%20of%20the%20Union%20address%20in%20February%2C%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20clarified%20that%20%E2%80%98the%20US%20seeks%20competition%2C%20not%20conflict.%E2%80%99%20Worse%2C%20there%20is%20no%20clarity%20on%20what%20the%20competition%20should%20deliver.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20most%20agree%20that%20like%20the%20Soviet%20Union%20during%20the%20Cold%20War%2C%20disintegration%20of%20China%20cannot%20be%20the%20end-state%20%E2%80%93%20especially%20since%20it%20is%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20manufacturing%20hub%20and%20happens%20to%20be%20the%20primary%20trading%20partner%20of%20nearly%20138%20nations.%20Despite%20tensions%2C%20the%20total%20value%20in%20goods%20trade%20between%20the%20US%20and%20China%20in%202022-2023%20stood%20at%20US%24%20690%20billion.%20So%2C%20the%20ideal%20end-state%20from%20the%20US%E2%80%99s%20point%20of%20view%20is%20one%20where%20there%20is%20a%20distinctive%20tilt%20in%20the%20balance%20of%20power%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20US%20and%20its%20allies%2F%20partners.%20This%20requires%20a%20new%20Cold%20War%20where%20the%20US%20plays%20to%20its%20advantage%3A%20military%20power%20or%20deterrence.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThus%2C%20the%20Biden%20administration%20has%20adopted%20a%20four-pronged%20approach.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%2C%20while%20overplaying%20the%20Chinese%20theft%20of%20US%20cutting-edge%20technologies%20by%20cyber%20means%2C%20Washington%20has%20adopted%20a%20%E2%80%98small%20yard%20and%20high%20fence%E2%80%99%20strategy%20to%20deny%20advanced%20processors%20(7nm%20and%20below)%20to%20China.%20According%20to%20the%20US%2C%20China%20will%20use%20these%20advanced%20microchips%20for%20new%20breakthroughs%20in%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20(AI)%2C%20quantum%20computing%20and%20biotechnology%20to%20threaten%20its%20and%20its%E2%80%99%20allies%E2%80%99%20national%20security.%20The%20reality%20is%20that%20the%20US%2C%20which%20led%20the%20world%20in%20the%20third%20industrial%20revolution%20by%20semiconductors%2C%20mainframe%20computers%2C%20personal%20computers%2C%20and%20the%20internet%2C%20worries%20that%20China%20could%20leapfrog%20in%20the%20fourth%20industrial%20revolution%20with%20AI%20and%20data%20since%205G%20wireless%20connectivity%2C%20which%20is%20the%20backbone%20of%20this%20revolution%2C%20has%20already%20been%20rolled%20out%20by%20China%E2%80%99s%20Huawei.%20This%20could%20make%20China%20the%20leader%20in%20setting%20international%20standards%20for%20the%20whole%20range%20of%20emerging%20technologies%20across%20the%20physical%2C%20digital%20and%20biological%20domains.%20Moreover%2C%20to%20ensure%20on-shoring%20and%20friendly-shoring%20of%20an%20advanced%20AI%20hardware%20ecosystem%2C%20the%20US%20passed%20the%20Chips%20and%20Science%20Act%2C%20Inflation%20Reduction%20Act%20and%20the%20Infrastructure%20Investment%20and%20Jobs%20Act%20to%20protect%20its%20advantages.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETwo%2C%20the%20US%20is%20strengthening%20its%20deterrence%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20region%20by%20reinforcing%20existing%20alliances%2C%20and%20by%20forming%20new%20one%E2%80%99s%20like%20AUKUS%20(Australia%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20the%20US).%20Called%20Integrated%20Deterrence%2C%20this%20includes%20a%20strategic%20partnership%20with%20India%20(given%20its%20sensitive%20location%20in%20the%20Indo%20Pacific)%20bilaterally%20%E2%80%93%20via%20the%20US-India%20Initiative%20on%20Critical%20and%20Emerging%20Technologies%20(ICET)%20%E2%80%93%20and%20multilaterally%20through%20the%20QUAD%20(quadrilateral%20security%20grouping%20of%20US%2C%20India%2C%20Japan%2C%20and%20Australia).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThree%2C%20to%20meet%20the%20military%20challenge%20of%20China%20and%20Russia%20combine%2C%20the%20US%20has%20connected%20its%20alliances%20in%20Europe%20with%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20by%20globalising%20NATO.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFour%2C%20to%20showcase%20that%20its%20balancing%20against%20China%20has%20both%20military%20and%20economic%20initiatives%2C%20the%20US%20has%20announced%20numerous%20international%20infrastructure%20building%20agreements%20like%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20Economic%20Framework%2C%20Build%20Back%20Better%20World%2C%20and%20the%20recent%20India-Middle%20East-Europe%20Economic%20Corridor.%20The%20truth%20is%20that%20none%20come%20close%20to%20the%20BRI%20where%20China%2C%20through%20the%20Asian%20Infrastructure%20Investment%20Bank%2C%20Silk%20Road%20Fund%2C%20China%20Development%20Bank%2C%20and%20Exim%20Bank%20has%20already%20invested%20US%24%20one%20trillion.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20the%20above%20military%20steps%2C%20the%20US%20hopes%20to%20disallow%20free%20movement%20to%20the%20People%E2%80%99s%20Liberation%20Army%20(PLA)%20within%20the%20First%20Island%20Chain%20in%20the%20west%20Pacific%20where%20China%20has%20two%20of%20its%20total%20three%20core%20concerns%3A%20Taiwan%20and%20South%20China%20Sea%20(SCS)%3B%20the%20third%20being%20India%E2%80%99s%20state%20of%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20which%20China%20calls%20south%20Tibet%20or%20Zangnan.%20With%20growing%20PLA%20capabilities%2C%20China%20has%20taken%20a%20strong%20stand%20against%20US%20freedom%20of%20navigation%20and%20air%20patrols%20in%20the%20SCS%20and%20its%20arming%20of%20Taiwan.%20While%20most%20analysts%20believe%20that%20the%20west%20Pacific%20theatre%20is%20a%20likely%20flash%20point%20between%20the%20US%20and%20China%2C%20it%20appears%20unlikely.%20Great%20powers%20do%20not%20go%20to%20war%20directly%20since%20neither%20will%20be%20able%20to%20exercise%20enough%20war%20control%20to%20achieve%20desired%20military%20objectives%2C%20nor%20have%20escalation%20control%20to%20limit%20war.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInterestingly%2C%20with%20US%20involvement%20in%20Ukraine%20(by%20proxy)%20and%20directly%20in%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20war%2C%20Washington%20will%20now%20have%20difficulty%20in%20devoting%20time%20and%20resources%20to%20its%20primary%20and%20pacing%20threat%E2%80%94China.%20Worse%2C%20the%20chances%20of%20US%20credibility%20taking%20a%20hit%20in%20both%20regional%20wars%20are%20high%20since%20they%20are%20unlikely%20to%20end%20in%20its%20favour.%20President%20Zelenskyy%20of%20Ukraine%20is%20feeling%20the%20heat%20since%20US%20arms%20supplies%20are%20getting%20diverted%20to%20its%20closest%20ally%2C%20Israel.%20Moreover%2C%20Russia%20is%20already%20in%20possession%20of%2023%20per%20cent%20of%20Ukrainian%20territory%20and%20is%20likely%20to%20occupy%20more%20before%20the%20war%20ends%20in%20temporary%20peace.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Israel-Palestine%20conflict%20presents%20the%20US%20with%20a%20big%20dilemma%20since%20it%20cannot%20abandon%20this%20war%20which%20while%20threatening%20to%20enlarge%20into%20a%20wider%20Middle%20East%20confrontation%2C%20has%20no%20solution%20in%20sight.%20Israel%20is%20not%20going%20to%20accept%20the%20two-state%20solution%20and%20the%20Muslim%20world%20will%20reject%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20plan%20to%20push%20some%202.3%20million%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza%20into%20the%20Sinai%20in%20Egypt.%20With%20each%20day%2C%20the%20credibility%20of%20China%20and%20Russia%20is%20rising%20in%20the%20region%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20the%20US.%20Worse%2C%20US%20allies%20and%20partners%20in%20east%20Asia%20watching%20the%20two%20regional%20wars%20might%20start%20assessing%20the%20US%20as%20an%20unreliable%20security%20partner.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThus%2C%20even%20as%20the%20US%E2%80%99s%20new%20Cold%20War%20in%20a%20fragmented%20world%20is%20unfolding%2C%20China%E2%80%99s%20strategy%20of%20%E2%80%98cooperation%20in%20an%20interdependent%20world%E2%80%99%20with%20BRI%20as%20its%20roadmap%20is%20gaining%20greater%20acceptability%20amongst%20Global%20South%20nations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EConscious%20of%20this%2C%20Xi%2C%20at%20the%203%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Erd%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20BRF%20announced%20the%20next%20phase%20of%20the%20BRI%E2%80%99s%20strategy%20called%20%E2%80%98small%2C%20yet%20smart.%E2%80%99%20While%20earmarking%20US%24%20107%20billion%20for%20the%20next%20five%20years%2C%20Xi%20said%20that%20the%20BRI%E2%80%99s%20focus%20will%20be%20on%20projects%20involving%20science%20and%20technology.%20He%20was%20referring%20to%20taking%20most%20BRI%20nations%20into%20the%20third%20and%20fourth%20industrial%20revolutions%20depending%20upon%20their%20level%20of%20development.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGiven%20this%20new%20strategy%2C%20Xi%20highlighted%20four%20areas%20of%20partnership.%20First%2C%20Xi%20announced%20a%20new%20initiative%20called%20%E2%80%98Global%20AI%20Governance%20Initiative%E2%80%99%2C%20his%20fourth%20in%2010%20years%20of%20BRI%3B%20the%20other%20three%20being%20the%20Global%20Development%20Initiative%2C%20Global%20Security%20Initiative%2C%20and%20Global%20Civilisation%20Initiative.%20The%20present%20initiative%20involving%20AI%20and%20data%20would%20be%20done%20in%20partnership%20with%20the%20BRI%20nations.%20China%20will%20set%20the%20technology%20standards%2C%20while%20Chinese%20companies%20in%20partnership%20with%20host%20nations%20will%20determine%20rules%2C%20regulations%2C%20and%20norms%20for%20use%20of%20emerging%20technologies%20for%20development.%20Thus%2C%20China%20will%20help%20set%20up%20data%20centres%2C%20cloud%20services%2C%20and%20a%20whole%20range%20of%20AI%20activities%20like%20data%20collection%2C%20algorithm%20design%2C%20technology%20development%2C%20technology%20production%2C%20and%20applications.%20To%20facilitate%20the%20applications%2C%20Xi%20proposed%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fmprc.gov.cn%2Fmfa_eng%2Fzxxx_662805%2F202310%2Ft20231020_11164505.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esetting%20up%20of%20100%2C000%20%E2%80%98training%20opportunities%E2%80%99%20in%20BRI%20nations%20by%202030%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20level%20of%20industrial%20internet%20development%20presupposes%20that%20advancement%20in%20third%20industrial%20revolution%20with%20Chinese%20help%20would%20be%20underway%20or%20completed%20in%20three%20specific%20areas%3A%20fibre%20optic%20cables%2C%20sea%20cables%2C%20and%20Chinese%20Baidu%20global%20satellite%20system.%20Unlike%20the%20US%E2%80%99s%20Global%20Position%20System%20with%2031%20satellites%2C%20the%20Baidu%20system%20is%20a%20constellation%20of%2045%20satellites%20with%20ability%20for%20two-way%20beaming%2C%20which%20means%20that%20in%20the%20remotest%20areas%20where%20satellite%20ground%20stations%20are%20not%20available%2C%20communication%20can%20be%20done%20directly%20between%20sender%20and%20receiver%20through%20satellite.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESecond%2C%20to%20mitigate%20climate%20change%20disasters%2C%20China%20has%20proposed%20green%20development%20for%20BRI%20nations.%20This%20is%20doable%20since%20China%20is%20a%20world%20leader%20in%20solar%20panels%2C%20electric%20vehicles%2C%20and%20Lithium-ion%20batteries.%20The%20latter%20will%20soon%20be%20supplemented%20by%20Sodium-ion%20batteries%2C%20which%20while%20cheaper%20than%20Lithium-ion%20batteries%20will%20give%20similar%20results.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThird%2C%20connectivity%20with%20focus%20on%20rail%20links%20with%20the%20China-Europe%20Railway%20Express%20as%20the%20flagship%20project.%20Once%20again%2C%20China%20is%20a%20global%20leader%20in%20rail%20connectivity%20and%20has%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20high%20speed%20%E2%80%93%20350km%2Fhour%20%E2%80%93%20network.%20Moreover%2C%20in%20June%202021%2C%20China%20successfully%20showcased%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20first%20MagLev%20(Magnetic%20Levitation)%20train%20with%20600km%2Fhour%20speed.%20By%202025%2C%20China%20will%20have%20five%20more%20Maglev%20trains%20which%20it%20has%20proposed%20to%20be%20an%20intermediate%20mode%20of%20travel%20between%20railways%20and%20commercial%20aeroplanes.%20The%20moot%20point%20is%20that%20by%20setting%20standards%20in%20AI%2C%20fast%20rails%2C%20and%20green%20development%20in%20BRI%20nations%2C%20China%20will%20have%20an%20unbeatable%20lead%20in%20international%20standards%20setting%20which%20will%20provide%20first%20user%20advantage%20to%20Chinese%20companies%20in%20Global%20South%20nations%2C%20and%20later%2C%20most%20of%20the%20world.%20And%20fourth%2C%20Xi%20expressed%20the%20need%20for%20establishing%20a%20BRI%20secretariat%2C%20which%2C%20given%20the%20increasing%20footprint%20of%20BRI%20plus%20Greater%20Eurasia%20nations%2C%20would%20be%20necessary.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20for%20making%20Greater%20Eurasia%20a%20reality%2C%20Putin%20spoke%20at%20the%20BRF%20about%20the%20urgency%20to%20develop%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20far%20east%20by%20opening%20the%20Northern%20Sea%20route%20which%20provides%20the%20shortest%20shipping%20lane%20from%20Europe%20to%20East%20Asia%20through%20the%20Bering%20Strait.%20According%20to%20Putin%2C%20starting%202024%2C%20ice-class%20cargo%20ships%20will%20be%20able%20to%20operate%20on%20this%20route%20round%20the%20year.%20Moreover%2C%20with%20Russia%20assuming%20the%20BRICS%20presidency%20in%202024%2C%20development%20of%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20far%20east%20from%20Vladivostok%20to%20East%20Cape%20will%20be%20a%20priority.%20This%20includes%20the%20Siberian%20and%20Sakhalin%20gas%20pipelines.%20After%20all%2C%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20Arctic%20which%20accounts%20for%2030%20per%20cent%20of%20its%20territory%20across%20three%20time%20zones%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iea.org%2Farticles%2Fenergy-fact-sheet-why-does-russian-oil-and-gas-matter%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehas%2020%20per%20cent%20of%20its%20oil%20and%2080%20per%20cent%20of%20its%20gas%20reserves.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20Russian%20Arctic%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Northern%20Sea%20route%20are%20being%20developed%20with%20Chinese%20help.%20Given%20this%2C%20joint%20naval%20patrols%20by%20Russian%20and%20Chinese%20navies%20in%20the%20Arctic%20region%20for%20peace%20and%20stability%20has%20raised%20US%20heckles%20as%20the%20Bering%20Strait%20runs%20close%20to%20Alaska.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20this%20area%20has%20become%20a%20region%20of%20great%20power%20contestation%2C%20it%20has%20become%20another%20impetus%20for%20the%20Chinese%20and%20Russian%20%E2%80%98no%20limits%E2%80%99%20partnership.%20Contrary%20to%20the%20belief%20that%20dislike%20of%20the%20US%20is%20the%20main%20reason%20for%20the%20Chinese%20and%20Russian%20partnership%2C%20it%20is%20the%20integration%20of%20their%20global%20visions%20which%20will%20see%20them%20working%20together%20in%20the%20foreseeable%20future.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWestern%20analysts%20wonder%20whether%20China%20and%20Russia%20will%20form%20an%20alliance%20like%20NATO%20where%20an%20attack%20on%20one%20will%20be%20considered%20an%20attack%20on%20all.%20This%20will%20not%20happen.%20Global%20powers%20like%20the%20US%2C%20China%2C%20and%20Russia%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20alliances%20among%20themselves.%20They%20have%20the%20capability%20to%20defend%20their%20own%20territorial%20integrity.%20Smaller%20powers%20seek%20alliances%20with%20major%20powers%20for%20collective%20security.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBesides%2C%20an%20alliance%20or%20military%20bloc%20runs%20against%20the%20spirit%20of%20global%20cooperation%20that%20China%20and%20Russia%20are%20collectively%20seeking.%20And%20that%20is%20how%20they%20are%20offering%20an%20alternate%20vision%20to%20the%20Global%20South%E2%80%94security%20through%20cooperation%20and%20interdependence.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EPravin%20Sawhney%E2%80%99s%20recent%20book%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Last%20War%3A%20How%20AI%20Will%20Shape%20India%E2%80%99s%20Final%20Showdown%20With%20China.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700105707000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16090026%2FUntitled-design-6-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fas-biden-and-xi-meet-whats-at-stake-is-two-competing-visions-for-the-world%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Global%20South%2C%20barring%20India%2C%20is%20increasingly%20attracted%20by%20China%E2%80%99s%20cooperation-driven%20approach%20to%20global%20development%20and%20put%20off%20by%20the%20US%E2%80%99s%20emphasis%20on%20competition%20and%20confrontation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fas-biden-and-xi-meet-whats-at-stake-is-two-competing-visions-for-the-world%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIt%20Was%20Used%20Wicket%2C%20But...%26quot%3B%3A%20Kane%20Williamson%20On%20'Pitch%20Swap%20Controversy'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERight%20before%20the%20start%20of%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20semi-final%20between%20India%20and%20New%20Zealand%2C%20a%20controversy%20hit%20the%20cricketing%20world%2C%20with%20the%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20being%20accused%20of%20changing%20the%20pitch%20at%20the%20last%20minute.%20There%20were%20suggestions%20that%20India%20made%20the%20change%20in%20order%20to%20tilt%20the%20equation%20in%20their%20favour%20a%20little.%20When%20New%20Zealand%20skipper%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Kane%20Williamson%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1058-kane-williamson-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKane%20Williamson%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20asked%20about%20the%20same%20in%20the%20post-match%20press%20conference%2C%20he%20played%20down%20the%20chatter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWilliamson%2C%20in%20the%20presser%2C%20admitted%20that%20it%20was%20a%20used%20wicket%20but%20since%20it%20was%20a%20good%20one%2C%20New%20Zealand%20had%20no%20objection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%2C%20I%20mean%2C%20yeah%20it%20was%20a%20used%20wicket%2C%20but%20a%20pretty%20good%20surface%20really%2C%20as%20we%20saw.%20I%20mean%2C%20they%20got%20plenty%20out%20of%20it%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%20the%20match.%20And%20conditions%2C%20I%20guess%20they%20change%20as%20they%20go%20under%20lights%20and%20things%2C%20and%20that's%20what%20we've%20seen%20throughout%20this%20competition.%20That's%20fine%2C%20that's%20what%20you%20expect%20and%20they%20played%20really%20well.%20So%20yeah%2C%20I%20mean%20it's%20disappointing%20to%20get%20to%20this%20stage%20and%20not%20go%20further%2C%20but%20also%20at%20the%20same%20time%20you%20sort%20of%20reflect%20on%20the%20seven%20weeks%20rather%20than%20a%20couple%20of%20small%20moments%20and%20we%20lost%20to%20a%20better%20side%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20responding%20to%20a%20reporter's%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWilliamson%20also%20called%20India%20'the%20best%20team%20in%20the%20world'%2C%20saying%20they%20will%20enter%20the%20final%20full%20of%20confidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20the%20best%20team%20in%20the%20world%20and%20they're%20all%20playing%20their%20best%20cricket%2C%20so%20that's%20tough.%20And%20I%20think%20we%20see%20in%20cricket%20-%20often%20it's%20surrounded%20with%20failure%20and%20how%20you%20deal%20with%20it.%20The%20way%20they've%20played%20throughout%20this%20tournament%20has%20been%20incredible.%20They%20haven't%20missed%20a%20beat%20really%20and%20to%20come%20into%20a%20semi-final%2C%20you%20go%20through%20your%20round-robin%20and%20you%20try%20and%20get%20to%20the%20stage%20and%20it%20starts%20again%20but%20the%20way%20they%20came%20out%20and%20played%2C%20yeah%2C%20shows%20the%20mindset%20that%20they%20have%20and%20the%20space%20that%20they're%20in%20and%20I've%20got%20no%20doubt%20they'll%20go%20into%20that%20next%20match%20full%20of%20confidence%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Kiwi%20skipper.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700105460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fh42tejfg_kane-williamson-pc_625x300_16_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fit-was-used-wicket-but-kane-williamson-shuts-down-pitch-swap-controversy-talks-4578070%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kane%20Williamson%20played%20down%20the%20chatter%20around%20the%20'pitch%20swap%20controversy'%2C%20despite%20admitting%20that%20the%20India%20vs%20New%20Zealand%20World%20Cup%20semi-final%20was%20played%20on%20a%20used%20surface.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A127%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fit-was-used-wicket-but-kane-williamson-shuts-down-pitch-swap-controversy-talks-4578070%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fit-was-used-wicket-but-kane-williamson-shuts-down-pitch-swap-controversy-talks-4578070%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fit-was-used-wicket-but-kane-williamson-shuts-down-pitch-swap-controversy-talks-4578070%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UNSEEN%20pics%20from%20PeeCee-Nick's%20Diwali%20party%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700105426000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105248737%2Cimgsize-67856.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Funseen-pics-f