0to%20congratulate%20them%20about%20%3Cem%3EGadar%202%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Kareena%20said%20promptly%2C%20%26quot%3BNo%20but%20I%20think%20that%20it's%20just%20fabulous%20and%20I%20can%20congratulate%20them%20now%2C%20here.%26quot%3B%20She%20also%20admitted%20that%20she%20hadn't%20watched%20%3Cem%3EGadar%202%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20see%20the%20film%2C%20I%20really%20want%20to.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EKaho%20Naa%E2%80%A6%20Pyaar%20Hai%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20released%20in%202000%2C%20was%20directed%20by%20Rakesh%20Roshan%20and%20launched%20the%20careers%20of%20both%20his%20son%20Hrithik%20and%20Ameesha.%20It%20was%20originally%20meant%20to%20star%20Kareena%20Kapoor%20who%20exited%20the%20film%20and%20instead%20made%20her%20debut%20in%20%3Cem%3ERefugee%3C%2Fem%3E%20with%20Abhishek%20Bachchan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20Ameesha%20Patel%20made%20headlines%20by%20telling%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DkEa17kAvsSo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBollywood%20Bubble%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Kareena%20had%20not%20quit%20the%20film%20of%20her%20own%20volition%20but%20had%20been%20ousted%20by%20Rakesh%20Roshan.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fameesha-patel-on-kareena-kapoors-exit-from-kaho-naa-pyaar-hai-rakesh-ji-asked-her-to-leave-4354993%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BActually%2C%20she%20didn't%20back%20out.%3C%2Fa%3E%20From%20what%20Rakesh%20ji%20told%20me%2C%20he%20asked%20her%20to%20leave%20the%20film%20because%20they%20were%20having%20differences.%20Pinkie%20%5BRoshan%5D%20aunty%2C%20his%20wife%20and%20Hrithik's%20mom%2C%20said%20that%20they%20were%20shocked%20because%20the%20set%20was%20ready%2C%20and%20a%20replacement%20Sonia%20had%20to%20be%20found%20in%20three%20days%2C%20and%20crores%20of%20rupees%20(had%20been%20spent)%20on%20that%20set%2C%20and%20it%20was%20Hrithik's%20debut%20and%20everyone%20was%20stressed%2C%26quot%3B%20she%2