a%20video%2C%20the%20Israel%20army%20showed%20automatic%20weapons%2C%20grenades%2C%20ammunition%2C%20and%20flak%20jackets%20it%20said%20were%20recovered%20from%20the%20hospital%20complex.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BTonight%20we%20conducted%20a%20targeted%20operation%20into%20Shifa%20Hospital.%20We%20continue%20to%20move%20forward%2C%26quot%3B%20Major%20General%20Yaron%20Finkelman%2C%20head%20of%20Israeli%20military%20operations%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20said%20on%20the%20army's%20Telegram%20channel.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIsrael%20has%20repeatedly%20accused%20Hamas%20of%20building%20a%20command%20centre%20in%20a%20tunnel%20network%20underneath%20the%20hospital%20-%20a%20claim%20the%20US%20says%20its%20own%20intelligence%20supports%20but%20Hamas%20denies.%20The%20Israeli%20Defence%20forces%20made%20no%20mention%20of%20finding%20any%20tunnel%20entrances%20in%20al%20Shifa%20after%20their%20searches.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Palestinean%20health%20ministry%20said%20that%20Israel%20has%20deployed%20bulldozers%20around%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20United%20Nations%20estimates%20that%20at%20least%202%2C300%20patients%2C%20staff%2C%20and%20displaced%20civilians%20are%20inside%20the%20hospital%2C%20including%2036%20newborns.%20Three%20premature%20babies%20died%20last%20week%20after%20the%20institution%20ran%20out%20of%20fuel%20to%20keep%20the%20incubators%20going.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20al%20Shifa%20hospital%20director%20yesterday%20said%20water%2C%20electricity%2C%20and%20oxygen%20to%20all%20departments%20was%20cut%20off%20as%20the%20Israeli%20troops%20stormed%20into%20the%20premises.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EInternational%20concern%20over%20Israel's%20attack%20on%20civilians%20in%20Gaza%20has%20increased%20since%20news%20of%20Israel's%20raid%20on%20the%20hospital%20emerged.%20%26quot%3BThe%20protection%20of%20newborns%2C%20patients%2C%20medical%20staff%2C%20and%20all%20civilians%20must%20override%20all%20other%20concerns.%20Hospitals%20are%20