-at-the-peak-of-her-career-heres-what-she-replied%2Farticleshow%2F105247777.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Day%205%20Of%20Tunnel%20Rescue%20Op%2C%20Food%2C%20Medicines%20Given%20To%2040%20Stuck%20For%2096%20Hours%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERescue%20operations%20to%20evacuate%2040%20construction%20workers%20trapped%20under%20debris%20at%20a%20collapsed%20tunnel%20in%20Uttarakhand's%20Uttarkashi%20district%20entered%20Day%205%20today.%20For%20over%2096%20hours%2C%20the%20workers%20have%20been%20confined%20within%20the%20tunnel%2C%20their%20lives%20hanging%20by%20a%20thread.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%2012%2C%20the%20Silkyara%20Tunnel%20project%20suffered%20a%20collapse%2C%20trapping%2040%20construction%20workers%20within%20the%20rubble.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trapped%20workers%20are%20being%20provided%20with%20essential%20supplies%20of%20food%20and%20medicines.%20Rescue%20teams%20are%20maintaining%20regular%20communication%20with%20the%20workers%2C%20ensuring%20their%20spirits%20remain%20unbroken%20and%20their%20hope%20alive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElite%20rescue%20teams%20from%20Thailand%20and%20Norway%2C%20including%20the%20one%20that%20successfully%20rescued%20the%20trapped%20children%20from%20a%20cave%20in%20Thailand%20in%202018%2C%20have%20joined%20forces%20to%20aid%20in%20the%20ongoing%20rescue%20operation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deployment%20of%20an%20'American%20auger'%20machine%20inside%20the%20tunnel%20marked%20a%20turning%20point%20in%20the%20rescue%20operation.%20This%20specialised%20equipment%20is%20anticipated%20to%20accelerate%20the%20clearing%20process%20and%20bring%20the%20trapped%20workers%20closer%20to%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'American%20auger'%20machine%20arrived%20in%20disassembled%20components%20at%20the%20Chinyalisaur%20airport%2C%20situated%20over%2030%20kilometres%20from%20the%20collapsed%20tunnel%20on%20the%20Char%20Dham%20pilgrimage%20route.%20The%20plan%20involves%20employing%20the%20machine%20to%20excavate%20a%20passage%20through%20the%20debris%20of%20the%20collapsed%20tunnel%20section.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20passage%20is%20clear%2C%20800-mm%20and%20900-mm%20diametre%20segments%20of%20mild%20steel%20pipes%20will%20be%20installed%2C%20one%20at%20a%20time.%20Upon%20completion%20of%20this%20procedure%2C%20the%20workers%20trapped%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20rubble%20will%20be%20able%20to%20crawl%20to%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYesterday%2C%20the%20rescue%20operations%20were%20hindered%20by%20a%20fresh%20landslide%20after%20over%2070%20hours%20of%20relentless%20operations.%20Rescue%20teams%20had%20invested%20hours%20in%20constructing%20a%20platform%20for%20the%20'American%20auger'%2C%20however%2C%20the%20fresh%20landslide%20forced%20them%20to%20disassemble%20the%20machine%20and%20restart%20platform%20construction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Challenges%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20expert%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarakhand-tunnel-char-dham-project-soft-rocks-sinking-ground-experts-flag-challenges-in-tunnel-rescue-op-4575488%5C%22%3Espeaking%20to%20NDTV%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20highlighted%20the%20complexities%20of%20constructing%20infrastructure%20projects%20in%20the%20Himalayan%20region.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Sudhir%20Krishna%2C%20a%20former%20secretary%20at%20the%20Union%20Urban%20Development%20Ministry%2C%20has%20identified%20several%20challenges%20hindering%20the%20rescue%20of%20the%20construction%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHimalayan%20region%20comprises%20soft%20rocks%20in%20general.%20Only%20in%20patches%2C%20there%20are%20hard%20stable%20rocks.%20It's%20a%20difficult%20situation.%20There%20are%20multiple%20challenges%20(in%20rescue%20work)%2C%20landslide%20is%20one%2C%20land%20subsidence%20is%20the%20second%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Krishna%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubsidence%20is%20the%20gradual%20settling%20or%20downward%20movement%20of%20the%20Earth's%20surface%2C%20often%20caused%20by%20the%20removal%20of%20water%2C%20oil%2C%20natural%20gas%2C%20or%20minerals%20through%20mining%20or%20other%20acitivities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20state%20government%20or%20the%20centre%20cannot%20do%20it%20alone.%20They%20have%20to%20work%20together%20along%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20experts%20who%20have%20a%20vision.%20For%20example%2C%20this%20project%20is%20intended%20to%20reduce%20travel%20time%20from%2050%20minutes%20to%20five%20minutes%2C%20allowing%20two-way%20traffic%2C%20allowing%20SUVs%20to%20ply.%20What%20is%20the%20great%20hurry%3F%2050%20minutes%20is%20not%20a%20long%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Krishna%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20under-construction%20tunnel%20is%20part%20of%20the%20ambitious%20Char%20Dham%20project%2C%20a%20national%20infrastructure%20initiative%20to%20enhance%20connectivity%20to%20the%20Hindu%20pilgrimage%20sites%20of%20Badrinath%2C%20Kedarnath%2C%20Gangotri%2C%20and%20Yamunotri.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700103660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F44ba8r8g_uttarakhand-tunnel-pti-_625x300_16_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarakhand-tunnel-collapse-day-5-of-tunnel-rescue-op-food-medicines-given-to-40-stuck-for-96-hours-4578041%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rescue%20operations%20to%20evacuate%2040%20construction%20workers%20trapped%20under%20debris%20at%20a%20collapsed%20tunnel%20in%20Uttarakhand's%20Uttarkashi%20district%20entered%20Day%205%20today.%20For%20over%2096%20hours%2C%20the%20workers%20have%20been%20confined%20within%20the%20tunnel%2C%20their%20lives%20hanging%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarakhand-tunnel-collapse-day-5-of-tunnel-rescue-op-food-medicines-given-to-40-stuck-for-96-hours-4578041%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.o