%2C%20while%20demonstrating%20her%20lipstick%20hack%2C%20she%20revealed%20that%20Ranbir%20prefers%20the%20way%20she%20looks%20without%20lipstick%20and%20asks%20her%20to%20take%20it%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20been%20accused%20of%20talking%20too%20much%20about%20Ranbir%2C%26quot%3B%20Alia%20said%20on%20%3Cem%3EKoffee%20With%20Karan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20prompting%20host%20Karan%20Johar%20to%20ask%20about%20the%20recent%20controversy.%20%26quot%3BAnything%20you%20say%20about%20him%20becomes%20like%20a%20sudden%20explosion%20online%2C%26quot%3B%20KJo%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BIs%20it%20because%20Ranbir%20is%20not%20on%20social%20media%3F%26quot%3B%20Kareena%20Kapoor%20agreed%20instantly%20and%20so%20did%20Alia%20%E2%80%93%20Ranbir%20is%20not%20officially%20on%20social%20media%20though%20he%20does%20have%20a%20secret%20and%20private%20Instagram%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20so.%20I%20have%20a%20very%20candid%20way%20of%20speaking%20and%20even%20when%20I'm%20talking%20about%20something%20in%20my%20life%20I%20like%20to%20imitate%20the%20person%20I'm%20talking%20about%2C%20I%20like%20to%20give%20anecdotes%2C%20I%20like%20to%20make%20it%20personal%20and%20I%20feel%20like%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20things%20just%20get%20picked%20out%20of%20context.%20Which%20happened%20recently%20with%20a%20video%20and%20stuff%20like%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Alia%20Bhatt%20said.%20%26quot%3BMy%20team%20told%20me%20%3Cem%3Eyeh%20kuch%3C%2Fem%3E%20out%20of%20hand%20%3Cem%3Ejaa%20raha%20hain%3C%2Fem%3E%20(this%20is%20getting%20out%20of%20hand)%20and%20I%20said%20OK%20%3Cem%3Etheek%20hai%2C%20jaane%20do%3C%2Fem%3E%20because%20genuinely%20people%20say%20things%20all%20the%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20criticism%20of%20Ranbir%20Kapoor%20wasn't%20limited%20to%20social%20media%20comments.%20%26quot%3BBut%20then%20I%20realised%20there%20are%20serious%20articles%20talking%20about%20how%20he's%20a%20toxic%20man%20and%20this%20and%20that%20and%20I'm%20like%20are%20we%20serious%3F%20There%20are%20many%20issues%20in%20the%20world%20to%20give%20more%20attention%20toward%20than%20something%20I%20said%20in%20a%20completely%20different%20context.%20And%20I%20feel%20bad%20if%20people%20misunderstand%20it%20because%20he's%20genuinely%20the%20opposite%20of%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Alia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20comes%20with%20the%20territory%20of%20fame%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ERocky%20Aur%20Rani%20Kii%20Prem%20Kahaani%3C%2Fem%3E%20star%20admitted.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20line%20I%20feel%20is%20being%20crossed%20but%20you%20can't%20say%20anything%20about%20it%2C%20people%20can%20say%20what%20they%20want%20about%20you.%20In%20fact%20Ranbir%20says%20this%2C%20'Alia%20the%20audience%20owns%20you%2C%20they%20can%20say%20what%20the%20hell%20they%20want%20about%20you.%20As%20long%20as%20your%20movies%20are%20doing%20well%20please%20do%20not%20complain%20sitting%20in%20your%20apartment%20in%20Bandra.'%20I%20was%20like%2C%20ya%20that's%20right%2C%20%3Cem%3Ekuch%20mat%20bolo%3C%2Fem%3E%20(don't%20say%20anything)%2C%26quot%3B%20Alia%20Bhatt%20said..%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlia%20Bhatt%20and%20Ranbir%20Kapoor%20married%20last%20year%20in%20April%20and%20are%20parents%20to%20a%20daughter%20named%20Raha%20who%20recently%20celebrated%20her%20first%20birthday.%20Ranbir%20and%20Kareena%20Kapoor%20are%20cousins%20and%20belong%20to%20one%20of%20Bollywood's%20most%20prominent%20family%20of%20actors%20and%20filmmakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700101680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F05u76no_aliaranbir1200_625x300_16_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fkoffee-with-karan-8-alia-bhatt-on-ranbir-kapoor-being-seen-as-toxic-hes-genuinely-the-opposite-of-that-4578016%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Koffee%20With%20Karan%208%3A%20Alia%20Bhatt%20addressed%20the%20backlash%20about%20her%20comments%20on%20Ranbir%20Kapoor%20and%20lipstick%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22