2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1580-shami-ahmed-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMohammed%20Shami%3C%2Fa%3E's%20seven-wicket%20haul%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virat%20Kohli%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F967-virat-kohli-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVirat%20Kohli%3C%2Fa%3E's%20record%2050th%20ODI%20century%20were%20the%20highlights%20as%20India%20secured%20a%2070-wicket%20win%20over%20New%20Zealand%20in%20the%20semifinals%20of%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20at%20Wankhede%20Stadium%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20played%20a%20lot%20of%20cricket%20here%2C%20any%20score%20on%20this%20ground%2C%20you%20cannot%20relax.%20Got%20to%20get%20the%20job%20done%20quickly%20and%20stay%20at%20it.%20We%20knew%20there%20would%20be%20pressure%20on%20us.%20We%20were%20very%20calm%2C%20even%20though%20we%20were%20a%20bit%20sloppy%20on%20the%20field.%20These%20things%20are%20bound%20to%20happen%20(the%20partnership%20between%20Mitchell%20and%20Kane)%20but%20glad%20we%20could%20get%20the%20job%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rohit%20in%20the%20post-match%20presentation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20hard%20to%20say%20if%20we%20would%20have%20been%20in%20trouble%20%5Bhad%20India%20scored%2030-40%20less%5D.%20They%20would%20not%20have%20taken%20those%20risks.%20Williamson%20and%20Mitchell%20batted%20brilliantly.%20Was%20important%20for%20us%20to%20stay%20calm.%20The%20crowd%20went%20silent%2C%20but%20we%20knew%20we%20needed%20a%20catch%20or%20run%20out.%20Shami%20was%20brilliant.%20The%20form%20all%20the%20guys%20are%20in%2C%20top%20five-six%20batters%2C%20whenever%20they%20have%20gotten%20an%20opportunity%2C%20they%20have%20made%20it%20count.%20Very%20pleased%20to%20see%20what%20Iyer%20has%20done%20for%20us%20this%20tournament.%20Gill%2C%20the%20way%20he%20has%20batted%20for%20us%20has%20been%20brilliant.%20Unfortunately%2C%20he%20had%20to%20go%20off%20with%20cramps.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKohli%20did%20what%20he%20does%2C%20also%20got%20to%20his%20landmark%20century%20as%20well.%20England%20game%20we%20got%20230%20on%20the%20board%2C%20way%20bowlers%20bowled%20with%20the%20new%20ball%20was%20amazing.%20Today%20obviously%20being%20the%20semifinal%2C%20would%20not%20say%20there%20was%20no%20pressure%2C%20whenever%20you%20play%20there%20is%20pressure.%20Semifinal%20adds%20a%20bit%20extra%2C%20we%20wanted%20to%20not%20think%20too%20much%20about%20it%2C%20just%20do%20what%20we've%20been%20doing%20like%20in%20the%20first%20nine%20games.%20Things%20came%20off%20for%20us%20nicely%20in%20the%20second%20half%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20India%20opted%20to%20bat%20first%20and%20scored%20397%2F4%20in%20their%2050%20overs.%20Skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%20(47%20in%2029%20balls%2C%20with%20four%20boundaries%20and%20four%20sixes)%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shubman%20Gill%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F108578-shubman-gill-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShubman%20Gill%3C%2Fa%3E%20(80%20in%2066%20balls%2C%20with%20eight%20fours%20and%20three%20sixes)%20delivered%20a%20fine%20start%20with%20a%2071-run%20opening%20stand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVirat%20Kohli%20(117%20in%20113%20balls%2C%20nine%20fours%2C%20and%20two%20sixes)%20posted%20his%2050th%20ODI%20ton%2C%20while%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shreyas%20Iyer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64384-shreyas-santosh-iyer-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShreyas%20Iyer%3C%2Fa%3E%20(105%20in%2070%20balls%2C%20with%20four%20boundaries%20and%20eight%20sixes)%20scored%20his%20second-successive%20WC%20century%2C%20helping%20India%20post%20a%20massive%20score.%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22KL%20Rahul%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1688-lokesh-rahul-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKL%20Rahul%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20delivered%20a%2020-ball%20cameo%20of%2039%20runs%2C%20with%20five%20fours%20and%20two%20sixes.%3C%2Fp%3E