rring%20money.%20Individuals%20with%20family%20in%20Canada%20and%20Israel%20are%20being%20targeted%2C%20with%20fraudsters%20using%20AI%20to%20imitate%20the%20voice%20of%20the%20victim's%20relative%20in%20distress.%20The%20AI%20tool%20automatically%20adopts%20the%20targeted%20person's%20voice%2C%20which%20is%20often%20obtained%20from%20public%20sources%20such%20as%20social%20media%20or%20recordings.%20Experts%20advise%20people%20to%20double-check%20the%20urgency%20of%20the%20situation%20before%20transferring%20money%20and%20to%20be%20cautious%20when%20receiving%20calls%20from%20relatives%20in%20these%20countries.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22AMRITA%20DIDYALA%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%2C%20China%20Turning%20Back%20On%20Each%20Other%20Not%20An%20Option%3A%20Xi%20In%20Meet%20With%20Biden%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20shook%20hands%20Wednesday%20and%20pledged%20to%20reduce%20tensions%20as%20they%20met%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20a%20year%20at%20a%20high-stakes%20summit%20in%20California.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20smiling%20Biden%20greeted%20Xi%20after%20the%20Chinese%20leader%20stepped%20out%20of%20a%20black%20limousine%20at%20the%20scenic%20Filoli%20country%20estate%20in%20the%20California%20foothills%20near%20San%20Francisco%2C%20before%20the%20two%20leaders%20shook%20hands%20on%20the%20front%20steps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20leaders%20then%20headed%20inside%20for%20painstakingly%20choreographed%2C%20closed-door%20talks%20on%20issues%20including%20Taiwan%2C%20sanctions%20and%20trade%20that%20have%20roiled%20relations%20between%20the%20world's%20largest%20economies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20opened%20his%20remarks%20by%20saying%20that%20tensions%20should%20%26quot%3Bnot%20veer%20into%20conflict.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EXi%20responded%20by%20saying%20that%20%26quot%3Bturning%20their%20back%20on%20each%20other%20is%20not%20an%20option%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20superpowers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20was%20to%20give%20a%20solo%20press%20conference%20at%204%3A15%20pm%20(0015%20GMT%20Thursday)%20to%20discuss%20the%20summit%2C%20which%20was%20being%20held%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20APEC%20summit%20in%20San%20Francisco%2C%20the%20White%20House%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProtesters%20lined%20part%20of%20the%20route%20of%20Biden's%20motorcade%20from%20San%20Francisco%2C%20many%20with%20pro-Xi%20signs%20and%20red%20and%20yellow%20Chinese%20flags%20hung%20up%20on%20security%20fences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20officials%20have%20played%20down%20the%20chance%20of%20major%20breakthroughs%20although%20an%20agreement%20on%20restoring%20a%20hotline%20between%20the%20Chinese%20and%20US%20militaries%20on%20the%20cards%2C%20along%20with%20cooperation%20on%20stopping%20supplies%20of%20the%20drug%20fentanyl.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20main%20goal%20of%20the%20talks%20--%20which%20are%20taking%20place%20at%20the%20setting%20for%20the%20famed%201980s%20US%20soap%20opera%20%26quot%3BDynasty%26quot%3B%20--%20is%20to%20restore%20predictability%20to%20the%20relationship%2C%20US%20officials%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20time%20Biden%20and%20Xi%20met%20in%20person%20was%20in%20Bali%20in%20November%202022%2C%20and%20relations%20nosedived%20after%20the%20United%20States%20shot%20down%20an%20alleged%20Chinese%20spy%20balloon%20in%20February%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20'Tensions'%20-%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20talks%2C%20which%20come%20after%20months%20of%20delicate%20diplomatic%20negotiations%2C%20come%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20a%20long%20struggle%20for%20global%20primacy%20between%20the%20United%20States%20and%20an%20increasingly%20assertive%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20sensitive%20issues%20is%20Taiwan%2C%20the%20self-ruling%20democracy%20over%20which%20Beijing%20claims%20sovereignty%20and%20which%20it%20has%20not%20ruled%20out%20seizing%20by%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20was%20expected%20to%20tell%20Xi%20that%20the%20United%20States%20will%20stick%20to%20its%20%26quot%3BOne%20China%26quot%3B%20policy%20that%20emphasizes%20it%20does%20not%20support%20Taiwanese%20independence%2C%20but%20that%20it%20will%20continue%20to%20give%20Taiwan%20military%20aid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20do%20not%20want%20to%20see%20the%20tensions%20across%20the%20Taiwan%20Strait%20evolve%20into%20any%20kind%20of%20conflict%26quot%3B%2C%20White%20House%20National%20Security%20Council%20spokesman%20John%20Kirby%20told%20reporters%20hours%20before%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20was%20also%20expected%20to%20%26quot%3Braise%20concerns%20over%20human%20rights%20in%20China%26quot%3B%20including%20the%20repression%20of%20the%20Uyghur%20Muslim%20minority%2C%20added%20Kirby.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2080-year-old%20Biden%20held%20out%20an%20olive%20branch%20to%20Xi%2C%2070%2C%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20talks%2C%20insisting%20that%20the%20United%20States%20was%20%26quot%3Bnot%20trying%20to%20decouple%20from%20China%26quot%3B%20and%20wanted%20to%20improve%20the%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Biden%20could%20not%20resist%20adding%20at%20a%20fundraising%20dinner%20that%20under%20communist%20leader%20Xi%20China%20faced%20%26quot%3Breal%20problems%2C%26quot%3B%20while%20Biden%20claimed%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Breestablishing%20American%20leadership%20in%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20responded%20with%20a%20foreign%20ministry%20spokeswoman%20pointing%20out%20all%20countries%20had%20problems%2C%20including%20the%20United%20States%2C%20while%20sticking%20to%20positive%20talking%20points%20on%20the%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20'Important%20for%20everyone'%20-%3Cbr%3E%5CnExpectations%20of%20major%20announcements%20are%20low%20but%20the%20two%20countries%20have%20trailed%20a%20series%20of%20possible%20wins%20from%20Xi's%20first%20visit%20to%20US%20soil%20since%20he%20was%20hosted%20by%20then-president%20Donald%20Trump%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20is%20the%20restoration%20of%20the%20two%20countries'%20military%20hotline%2C%20which%20Beijing%20severed%20after%20then-House%20speaker%20Nancy%20Pelosi%20visited%20Taiwan%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20also%20hopes%20of%20%26quot%3Bprogress%26quot%3B%20on%20cooperation%20to%20limit%20Chinese%20exports%20of%20ingredients%20for%20fentanyl%2C%20the%20opioid%20drug%20sweeping%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20leaders%20were%20additionally%20expected%20to%20discuss%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict%20and%20the%20Ukraine%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20summit%2C%20China%20and%20the%20United%20States%20also%20pledged%20to%20work%20more%20closely%20together%20on%20global%20warming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%2C%20a%20partner%20of%20China%20in%20what%20Washington%20sees%20as%20a%20growing%20authoritarian%20alliance%2C%20welcomed%20the%20San%20Francisco%20meeting%2C%20with%20the%20Kremlin%20calling%20the%20talks%20%26quot%3Bimportant%20for%20everyone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20his%20part%20Xi%20was%20expected%20to%20push%20for%20an%20end%20to%20trade%20curbs%20and%20sanctions%2C%20with%20the%20Chinese%20economy%20struggling%20to%20shore%20up%20growth%20after%20its%20tough%20zero-Covid%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chinese%20leader%20was%20to%20host%20a%20dinner%20with%20US%20executives%20after%20the%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700100420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fpmf02o58_biden-xi-jinping_625x300_16_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-president-joe-biden-tells-xi-jinping-tensions-must-not-veer-into-conflict-4577878%22%2C%22summar