-7-the-race-to-preserve-israeli-soldiers-sperm%2F0000018b-af34-dea2-a9bf-ffbee1470000%5C%22%3Ebeen%20carried%20out%20on%2033%20men%20killed%20in%20Hamas%E2%80%99s%20cross-border%20raid%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20October%207%2C%20of%20which%2029%20were%20soldiers%20and%20the%20remaining%20four%20were%20civilians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20paper%20reported%20that%20the%20number%20of%20PSRs%20was%20rising%20but%20did%20not%20elaborate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlongside%20this%2C%20other%20news%20reports%2C%20including%20one%20from%20Bloomberg%2C%20stated%20that%20hundreds%20of%20Israeli%20women%20were%20volunteering%20not%20only%20to%20carry%20the%20embryo%20from%20the%20dead%20men%E2%80%99s%20sperm%20via%20invitro%20fertilisation%20(IVF)%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Ffeatures%2F2022-07-19%2Fsperm-extraction-technique-turns-dead-men-into-fathers%23xj4y7vzkg%5C%22%3Ebut%20also%20to%20mother%20children%20born%20thereafter%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20countries%20have%20outlawed%20PSR%2C%20but%20in%20Israel%20it%20is%20largely%20the%20parents%2C%20and%20not%20so%20much%20the%20widows%2C%20of%20the%20deceased%20young%20men%20who%20are%20fighting%20for%20their%20right%20to%20have%20grandchildren%2C%20a%20move%20which%20Bloomberg%20reported%20was%20triggering%20%E2%80%98raised%20eyebrows%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FNiMknPpcjKc%3Fsi%3DKQSMPnOvC-rcYBN9%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20service%20quoted%20Gil%20Siegal%2C%20head%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20Centre%20for%20Medical%20Law%2C%20Bioethics%20and%20Health%20Policy%2C%20as%20saying%20that%20it%20was%20in%20a%20child%E2%80%99s%20best%20interests%20to%20be%20born%20to%20living%20parents%2C%20and%20not%20in%20a%20state%20of%20%E2%80%9Cplanned%20orphanhood%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20the%20discourse%20around%20fertility%20and%20birth%20must%20%E2%80%9Cbegin%20with%20mother-father-child%2C%20not%20grandmother-grandfather-child%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20analysts%2C%20however%2C%20claimed%20that%20PSR%20was%20an%20undertaking%20aimed%20at%20spawning%20offspring%20who%20Siegal%20referred%20to%20as%20%E2%80%9Cliving%20monuments%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20almost%20all%20requests%20for%20PSR%20after%20last%20month%E2%80%99s%20Hamas%20attack%20had%20resulted%20in%20the%20Israeli%20health%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20legal%20adviser%20handing%20down%20a%20temporary%20order%2C%20by-passing%20the%20need%20for%20court%20approval%20to%20reap%20the%20deceased%E2%80%99s%20young%20men%E2%80%99s%20sperm%2C%20reported%20%3Cem%3EHaaretz%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPSR%20was%20first%20approved%20in%20Israel%20in%202003%20via%20%E2%80%98instructions%E2%80%99%20from%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20attorney%20general%20who%2C%20at%20the%20time%2C%20had%20declared%20that%20%E2%80%9Cprocreation%20%5Bwas%5D%20an%20important%20and%20substantive%20issue%20in%20Israeli%20society%E2%80%9D%20to%20which%20considerable%20emotional%20and%20financial%20resources%20were%20devoted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20also%20adhered%20to%20%E2%80%9Csociocultural%20values%E2%80%9D%20that%20promoted%20procreation%20even%20in%20the%20toughest%20circumstances%2C%20%3Cem%3EHaaretz%3C%2Fem%3E%20declared%2C%20but%20had%20passed%20no%20definitive%20legislation%20as%20yet%20regarding%20PSR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisraels-war-on-gaza-affirms-the-collapse-of-liberal-world-order%5C%22%3EIsrael%E2%80%99s%20War%20on%20Gaza%20Affirms%20the%20Collapse%20of%20Liberal%20World%20Order%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHence%2C%20when%20the%20Israel%20Defence%20Forces%20(IDF)%20informed%20a%20family%20about%20the%20death%20of%20their%20son%20in%20action%2C%20they%20also%20offered%20them%20the%20option%20of%20sperm%20preservation.%20Furthermore%2C%20the%20IDF%20helped%20the%20bereaved%20family%20contact%20the%20relevant%20parties%20for%20performing%20PSR%20as%20long%20as%20it%20was%20medically%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20experts%2C%20the%20best%20chance%20of%20finding%20living%20sperm%20is%20within%2024%20hours%20of%20death%2C%20after%20which%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20retrieve%2C%20and%20virtually%20impossible%20to%20collect%20after%20a%2072-hour%20hiatus.%20Searing%20local%20temperatures%20too%20adversely%20impact%20dead%20bodies%20in%20this%20regard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20subject%20%5Bof%20PSR%5D%20raises%20complex%20and%20ethical%20and%20legal%20questions%20%E2%80%A6%20as%20well%20as%20%5Bthe%20issue%20of%20its%5D%20psychological%20effects%20on%20the%20bereaved%20family%20and%20the%20bereaved%20family%E2%80%99s%20relationship%20with%20the%20spouse%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3EHaaretz%3C%2Fem%3E%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20complications%2C%20it%20said%2C%20centred%20on%20the%20proposed%20mother%20never%20having%20met%20the%20sperm%20donor%2C%20which%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20raised%20further%20questions%20regarding%20the%20legal%20and%20inheritance%20rights%20of%20the%20ensuing%20child%20or%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20of%2018%20or%2020-year-old%20IDF%20conscripts%20who%20died%20in%20battle%20or%20conflict%20also%20necessitated%20further%20deliberation%2C%20as%20their%20sperm%20would%20be%20inseminated%20into%20a%20unknown%20volunteer%2C%20initiating%20not%20only%20legal%2C%20but%20also%20psychological%20and%20emotional%20complications%20for%20all%20concerned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJailed%20Palestinians%2C%20too%2C%20look%20for%20ways%20to%20conceive%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Palestinians%20interned%20in%20Israeli%20jails%2C%20often%20for%20years%20at%20a%20time%2C%20were%20also%20locked%20in%20a%20partially%20successful%20effort%20at%20smuggling%20out%20their%20sperm%20to%20their%20spouses%20in%20Gaza%20to%20impregnate%20them%20via%20IVF.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20though%20there%20is%20no%20publicly%20available%20data%20on%20how%20many%20Palestinian%20couples%20had%20conceived%20in%20this%20manner%2C%20as%20it%20was%20a%20covert%20activity%20strictly%20monitored%20%E2%80%93%20and%20banned%20%E2%80%93%20by%20Israel%2C%20anecdotal%20accounts%20put%20their%20number%20at%20%E2%80%98a%20few%20score%E2%80%99%20over%20the%20past%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fy9t-qK-y1a0%3Fsi%3DWRHKccSG2hnSx4LL%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Washington-based%20%3Cem%3EAl-Monitor%3C%2Fem%3E%20news%20website%2C%20however%2C%20claims%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.al-monitor.com%2Foriginals%2F2021%2F02%2Fpalestinian-prisoners-israel-jails-smuggled-sperm-children.html%5C%22%3E96%20Palestinian%20children%20had%20been%20born%20via%20this%20clandestine%20process%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20the%20first%20such%20baby%20was%20conceived%20from%20smuggled%20sperm%20in%202012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%2096%20of%20them%2C%20it%20stated%2C%20had%20been%20dubbed%20%E2%80%9Cambassadors%20of%20freedom%E2%80%9D%2C%20as%20for%20Palestinians%20these%20teenagers%20were%20symbols%20of%20resistance%2C%20however%20meagre%2C%20against%20Israel%20in%20their%20enduring%20seven-decade%20long%20struggle%20for%20a%20homeland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20success%20rate%20of%20these%20surreptitious%20endeavours%20for%20Palestinians%20was%20highly%20restricted%2C%20compared%20to%20efficient%20Israeli%20PSR%20practices%20and%20follow-on%20storage%20processes%2C%20as%20live%20sperm%20had%20a%20limited%20life-span%20of%20up%20to%2012%20hours%2C%20after%20which%20it%20needed%20to%20be%20frozen%20to%20render%20it%20suitable%20for%20IVF.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsequently%2C%20its%20furtive%20journey%20from%20Israeli%20jails%20to%20Gaza%20in%20an%20assortment%20of%20ampules%20like%20vials%2C%20fountain%20pens%2C%20candy%20wrappers%2C%20chocolate%20bars%20and%20even%20the%20tips%20of%20rubber%20gloves%20stuffed%20with%20date%20paste%2C%20was%20invariably%20arduous%2C%20time%20consuming%20and%20predisposed%20to%20failure%20at%20every%20step%20of%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20included%20running%20the%20time-consuming%20gauntlet%20of%20Israeli%20checkpoints%20into%20Gaza%2C%20followed%20eventually%20by%20sperm%20fertilisation%2C%20all%20of%20which%20added%20up%20to%20an%20abysmally%20low%20birth%20rate%20for%20potential%20Palestinian%20%E2%80%98freedom%20ambassadors%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPalestinian%20spouses%20encountered%20yet%20another%20obstacle%20before%20undergoing%20IVF%20%E2%80%93%20inherent%20Muslim%20conservatism%20and%20practices%20required%20the%20doctor%20performing%20the%20procedure%20to%20have%20two%20members%20from%20the%20jailed%20husband%E2%80%99s%20family%20and%20an%20equal%20number%20from%20his%20wife%E2%80%99s%20to%20formally%20testify%20that%20the%20sperm%20was%20indeed%20%E2%80%98genuine%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlongside%20this%2C%20the%20concerned%20spouse%20was%20advised%20to%20advertise%20her%20impending%20pregnancy%2C%20as%20this%20helped%20avoid%20local%20gossip%20and%20insinuations%20suggesting%20infidelity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20June%202023%2C%20the%20Israel%20Prison%20Service%20was%20holding%204%2C499%20Palestinians%20in%20detention%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbc.ca%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fhamas-west-bank-palestine-1.7025163%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20Israeli%20Centre%20for%20Human%20Rights%20in%20the%20Occupied%20Territories%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20issue%20of%20prisoners%20was%20central%20to%20Palestinian%20society%2C%20which%20considered%20them%20freedom%20fighters%20resisting%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20occupation%20of%20the%20West%20Bank%20and%20near-constant%20blockade%20of%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrisoners%E2%80%99%20families%20were%20thus%20revered%2C%20receiving%20financial%20support%20from%20the%20Palestinian%20Authority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202022%2C%20the%20Australian%20Broadcasting%20Corporation%20(ABC)%20documented%20the%20instance%20of%20a%20woman%20named%20Farhana%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.abc.net.au%2Fnews%2F2022-01-02%2Fpalestinian-women-smuggle-sperm-from-imprisoned-husbands%2F100718618%5C%22%3Esuccessfully%20smuggling%20out%20a%20phial%3C%2Fa%3E%20containing%20her%20Palestinian%20husband%20Hossam%20Al%20Attar%E2%80%99s%20semen%20from%20an%20Israeli%20jail%2C%20where%20he%20was%20serving%20out%20an%2018-year%20sentence%2C%20till%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20series%20of%20setbacks%2C%20Farhana%20conceived%20and%20gave%20birth%20to%20her%20daughter%20Jannat%20%E2%80%93%20meaning%20heaven%20in%20Arabic%20%E2%80%93%20in%202014%2C%20amidst%20bombardment%20from%20Israeli%20combat%20aircraft%20during%20the%2050-day%20long%20Operation%20Protective%20Edge%E2%80%99s%20siege%20of%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20in%20which%20over%202%2C000%20Palestinians%20were%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20worth%20waiting%20all%20this%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%20ABC.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza%20are%20very%20pleased%20with%20this%20idea%20of%20smuggling%20sperm.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700098204000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F06180109%2Fcharles-eugene-6eEEsClXoNs-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fposthumous-sperm-retrieval-israel-palestine%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20program%20was%20first%20approved%20in%20Israel%20in%202003%20via%20%E2%80%98instructions