year%2C%20and%20wrapped%20up%20the%20four-hour%20summit%20with%20a%20walk%20in%20the%20garden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Xi%20and%20Biden%20remained%20far%20apart%20on%20the%20key%20flashpoint%20of%20Taiwan%2C%20with%20the%20Chinese%20president%20telling%20his%20US%20counterpart%20to%20stop%20arming%20the%20island%20and%20saying%20that%20reunification%20was%20%26quot%3Bunstoppable%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20sides%20announced%20a%20host%20of%20agreements%20after%20the%20talks%20at%20the%20Filoli%20Estate%20--%20where%20the%20soap%20opera%20%26quot%3BDynasty%26quot%3B%20was%20filmed%20in%20the%201980s%20--%20starting%20with%20the%20resumption%20of%20their%20high-level%20military%20hotline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20severed%20military-to-military%20communications%20after%20then%20House%20speaker%20Nancy%20Pelosi%20visited%20Taiwan%20in%202022.%20Beijing%20claims%20sovereignty%20over%20the%20self-ruling%20democracy%20and%20has%20not%20ruled%20out%20seizing%20it%20by%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20also%20agreed%20to%20tackle%20the%20production%20of%20ingredients%20for%20the%20drug%20fentanyl%2C%20responsible%20for%20a%20deadly%20epidemic%20of%20opioid%20abuse%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20officials%20on%20both%20sides%20said%20after%20the%20talks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20agreed%20to%20hold%20talks%20on%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20Chinese%20state%20media%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Veer%20into%20conflict'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20leaders%20had%20not%20met%20in%20person%20since%20they%20held%20talks%20in%20Bali%20in%20November%202022%2C%20and%20relations%20nosedived%20after%20the%20United%20States%20shot%20down%20an%20alleged%20Chinese%20spy%20balloon%20in%20February%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20Beijing%20and%20Washington%20have%20been%20engaged%20in%20intense%20diplomacy%20to%20get%20the%20two%20leaders%20face%20to%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20said%20talks%20had%20gone%20%26quot%3Bwell%26quot%3B%20and%20raised%20two%20thumbs%20up%20while%20he%20and%20Xi%20both%20waved%20at%20reporters%20as%20they%20strolled%20side-by-side%20in%20the%20grounds%20of%20the%20scenic%20country%20estate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20was%20due%20to%20give%20a%20press%20conference%20later%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20ensure%20that%20competition%20does%20not%20veer%20into%20conflict%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20US%20leader%20told%20Xi%20across%20a%20long%20wooden%20table%20as%20their%20delegations%20sat%20down%20for%20talks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EXi%20responded%20by%20saying%20that%20%26quot%3BPlanet%20Earth%20is%20big%20enough%20for%20the%20two%20countries%20to%20succeed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20two%20large%20countries%20like%20China%20and%20United%20States%2C%20turning%20their%20back%20on%20each%20other%20is%20not%20an%20option%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20initial%20session%20of%20talks%20and%20a%20working%20lunch%20of%20herbed%20ricotta%20ravioli%20and%20tarragon%20chicken%20with%20gold%20rice%20pilaf%2C%20Biden%20posted%20a%20brief%20update%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20value%20the%20conversation%20I%20had%20today%20with%20President%20Xi%20because%20I%20think%20it's%20paramount%20that%20we%20understand%20each%20other%20clearly%2C%20leader%20to%20leader%2C%26quot%3B%20Biden%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20critical%20global%20challenges%20that%20demand%20our%20joint%20leadership.%20And%20today%2C%20we%20made%20real%20progress.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETaiwan%20tensions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20on%20Taiwan%2C%20the%20rhetoric%20seemed%20to%20have%20barely%20moved%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina's%20foreign%20ministry%20said%20Xi%20had%20told%20Biden%20to%20%26quot%3Bstop%20arming%20Taiwan%20and%20support%20China's%20peaceful%20reunification.%20China%20will%20realize%20reunification%2C%20and%20this%20is%20unstoppable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20urged%20Xi%20to%20%26quot%3Brespect%26quot%3B%20upcoming%20elections%20in%20Taiwan%2C%20amid%20fears%20that%20the%20vote%20next%20year%20could%20become%20a%20new%20flashpoint%2C%20a%20US%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%2C%20a%20partner%20of%20China%20in%20what%20Washington%20sees%20as%20a%20growing%20authoritarian%20alliance%2C%20welcomed%20the%20meeting%2C%20with%20the%20Kremlin%20calling%20the%20talks%20%26quot%3Bimportant%20for%20everyone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20his%20part%2C%20Xi%20was%20expected%20to%20push%20for%20an%20end%20to%20trade%20curbs%2C%20with%20the%20Chinese%20economy%20struggling%20to%20shore%20up%20growth%20after%20its%20tough%20zero-Covid%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chinese%20leader%20was%20to%20host%20a%20dinner%20with%20US%20executives%20after%20the%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700095200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fv5bg8gu4_biden-xi-meeting_625x300_16_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjoe-biden-xi-jinping-agree-to-restart-high-level-military-talks-report-4577953%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chinese%20leader%20Xi%20Jinping%20and%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20agreed%20to%20restart%20high-level%20military-to-military%20talks%2C%20Beijing's%20state%20media%20said%20Thursday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjoe-biden-xi-jinping-agree-to-restart-high-level-military-talks-report-4577953%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjoe-biden-xi-jinping-agree-to-restart-high-level-military-talks-report-457795