t%20carrier%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F57dab3bcb0ef97f0288b5aa2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22586%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20MiG-29K%20lands%20on%20Indian%20navy%20aircraft%20carrier%20INS%20Vikramaditya%20in%202014.%3Cp%3EIndian%20Navy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Sukhoi%20design%20firm%20was%20working%20on%20the%20Su-33%20in%20the%201980s%2C%20the%20Mikoyan%20Design%20Bureau%20was%20working%20on%20its%20own%20carrier%20aircraft%2C%20the%20MiG-29K%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcombat-jets-russia-and-ukraine-are-using-in-ukraine-war-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enaval%20variant%20of%20the%20MiG-29%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWork%20on%20the%20MiG-29K%20was%20halted%20in%201991%20when%20the%20Russian%20navy%20selected%20the%20Su-33%20for%20its%20carriers%2C%20but%20the%20project%20was%20revived%20in%202004%20for%20the%20Indian%20navy%2C%20which%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnationalinterest.org%2Fblog%2Fbuzz%2Fall-reasons-why-india-hates-aircraft-carrier-it-bought-russia-92076%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eacquiring%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Kiev-class%20carrier%20Admiral%20Gorhskov%20from%20Russia%2C%20and%20wanted%20the%20jet%20for%20the%20carrier's%20air%20wing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20top%20speed%20of%20about%201%2C300%20mph%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20carry%209%2C900%20pounds%20of%20ordnance%2C%20the%20MiG-29K%20was%20better%20suited%20for%20ground%20strikes%20than%20the%20Su-33.%20India%20also%20chose%20the%20MiG-29K%20because%20its%20air%20force%20already%20operated%20the%20MiG-29%20and%20was%20familiar%20with%20the%20airframe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Indian%20navy%20MiG-29%20fighter%20jet%20aircraft%20carrier%20INS%20Vikrant%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F