0you%20have%20outside%20accountants%20involved%20in%20this%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20Flemmons%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJames%20and%20her%20team%20of%20lawyers%20would%20%E2%80%93%20and%20have%20%E2%80%93%20begged%20to%20differ.%20It's%20just%20like%20lying%20on%20your%20taxes%2C%20they%20have%20argued%20in%20court%20and%20in%20filings%3A%20You%20can't%20dodge%20legal%20responsibility%20by%20blaming%20your%20accountant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fdonald-trumps-accountants-quit-while-preparing-his-and-melanias-taxes-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrump's%20longtime%20accountant%20at%20Mazars%20USA%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20Donald%20Bender%2C%20has%20pointed%20his%20finger%20right%20back%20at%20Trump.%20Bender%20said%20in%20testimony%20last%20month%20that%20while%20his%20firm%20was%20responsible%20for%20compiling%20Trump's%20annual%20net-worth%20statements%2C%20it%20was%20up%20to%20Trump%20and%20his%20executives%20to%20provide%20him%20with%20accurate%20liability%20and%20market-value%20data%20to%20work%20from.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20the%20attorney%20general%20has%20alleged%2C%20Trump%20did%20not%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-organization-jurors-hear-tale-of-two-very-different-donalds-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BBlame%20the%20accountants%26quot%3B%20has%20been%20one%20of%20Trump's%20go-to%20defenses%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20his%20New%20York%20fraud%20travails%2C%20going%20back%20to%20the%20criminal%20payroll%20tax-fraud%20case%20his%20company%20lost%20a%20year%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJames%20is%20seeking%20a%20judge's%20verdict%20that%20would%20permanently%20ban%20Trump%20and%20his%20two%20eldest%20sons%20from%20running%20a%20business%20in%20New%20York.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-jr-learns-ny-wants-even-higher-fraud-penalties-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShe%20is%20also%20seeking%20at%20least%2