o-complaint.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elawsuit%3C%2Fa%3E%20filed%20in%20state%20Supreme%20Court%20aims%20to%20require%20PepsiCo%20and%20its%20subsidiaries%2C%20Frito-Lay%20Inc.%20and%20Frito-Lay%20North%20America%20Inc.%2C%20to%20clean%20up%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-of-the-global-population-wants-single-use-plastics-banned-2022-2%5C%22%3Esingle-use%20plastic%20packaging%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20food%20wrappers%20and%20plastic%20bottles%2C%20that%20have%20found%20a%20way%20to%20the%20shores%20of%20the%20Buffalo%20River%20and%20watershed%2C%20contaminating%20drinking%20water%20supply%20for%20the%20city%20of%20Buffalo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20company%20is%20too%20big%20to%20ensure%20that%20their%20products%20do%20not%20damage%20our%20environment%20and%20public%20health.%20All%20New%20Yorkers%20have%20a%20basic%20right%20to%20clean%20water%2C%20yet%20PepsiCo's%20irresponsible%20packaging%20and%20marketing%20endanger%20Buffalo's%20water%20supply%2C%20environment%2C%20and%20public%20health%2C%26quot%3B%20James%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fag.ny.gov%2Fpress-release%2F2023%2Fattorney-general-james-takes-historic-action-against-pepsico-endangering%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpepsi-says-people-skipping-meals-great-for-business-2023-10%5C%22%3EPepsiCo%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20the%20single%20largest%20identifiable%20contributor%20to%20the%20plastic%20waste%20contaminating%20the%20Buffalo%20River%2C%20according%20to%20the%20lawsuit.%20Of%20the%201%2C916%20pieces%20of%20plastic%20waste%20containing%20an%20identifiable%20brand%2C%2017.1%25%20were%20produced%20by%20PepsiCo%2C%20according%20to%20a%202022%20survey%20conducted%20by%20the%20state%20Office%20of%20the%20Attorney%20General.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmail%20messages%20left%20for%20a%20spokesperson%20at%20PepsiCo%20were%