f%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-dow-sees-death-cross-in-bearish-signal-2023-11%5C%22%3Etechnical%20sell%20signal%20that%20developed%20on%20Monday%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Dow%20Jones%20Industrial%20Average%20flashed%20a%20bearish%20%26quot%3Bdeath%20cross%26quot%3B%20on%20Monday%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-death-cross-bearish-technical-sp500-imminent-nasdaq-2022-3%5C%22%3Efor%20the%20first%20time%20since%20March%202022.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Bdeath%20cross%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20moving%20average%20crossover%20strategy%20employed%20by%20some%20traders%20and%20technical%20analysts%20as%20a%20signal%20to%20sell%20stocks.%20The%20signal%20occurs%20when%20the%20short-term%2050-day%20moving%20average%20crosses%20below%20the%20long-term%20200-day%20moving%20average.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lagging%20indicator%20can%20help%20alert%20traders%20to%20securities%20that%20are%20solidifying%20their%20downtrend%20and%20are%20likely%20to%20experience%20a%20continuation%20with%20lower%20stock%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20near%20700%20point%20rally%20in%20the%20Dow%20Jones%20Industrial%20Average%20since%20Monday%20was%20a%20big%20enough%20upside%20move%20to%20officially%20reverse%20the%20bearish%20death%20cross%20signal%20and%20spark%20a%20%26quot%3Bgolden%20cross%26quot%3B%20buy%20signal%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20Stockcharts.com.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Dow%20Jones%20Industrial%20Average's%2050-day%20moving%20average%20rose%20to%2033%2C827.04%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20less%20than%20a%20full%20point%20above%20the%20Dow%20Jones'%20200-day%20moving%20average%20of%2033%2C826.89.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221057%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dow%20gold%20cross%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655529af36d588dc55d11eeb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22448%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EStockcharts.com%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20golden%20cross%20signal%20is%20the%20exact%20opposite%20of%20a%20death%20cross%2C%20occurring%20when%20the%20short-term%2050-day%20moving%20average%20crosses%20above%20the%20long-term%20200-day%20moving%20average.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20short-term%20whiplash%20between%20the%20buy%20and%20sell%20signals%20highlights%20the%20lagging%20nature%20of%20these%20moving%20average%20crossover%20strategies%2C%20which%20have%20a%20tendency%20to%20generate%20false%20signals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20sometimes%20it%20doesn't%20pay%20to%20sell%20stocks%20after%20a%20bearish%20death%20cross%20or%20buy%20stocks%20after%20a%20bullish%20golden%20cross.%20In%20fact%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Ftechnical-death-cross-stock-market-sp500-historical-analysis-not-bad-2022-3%5C%22%3Ea%20historical%20analysis%20by%20Fundstrat%20of%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20death%20crosses%3C%2Fa%3E%20revealed%20that%20it%20pays%20to%20buy%20stocks%20after%20a%20death%20cross%2C%20rather%20than%20sell.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%2048%20occurrences%20since%201929%2C%20the%20average%20return%20on%20a%20three-%2C%20six-%2C%20and%2012-month%20timeframe%20were%20all%20positive%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%2280%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Findex%2Fs%26amp%3Bp_500%3Futm_medium%3Dingest%26utm_source%3Dmarkets%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%3ES%26amp%3BP%20500%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20an%20average%20three-month%20return%20of%202.1%25%2C%26quot%3B%20Fundstrat's%20Mark%20Newton%20said%20last%20year.%20What's%20more%2C%20the%20win%20rate%20for%20a%20positive%20return%20in%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20three%2C%20six%2C%20and%2012%20months%20after%20a%20death%20cross%20were%20all%20above%2050%25%2C%20according%20to%20the%20analysis.%3C%2F