Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20collectively%20resolved%20on%20the%20night%20before%20the%20scheduled%20public%20hearing%20on%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20October%2016%20held%20at%20Sunger%20Panchayat%2C%20Kashipur%20block%2C%20Rayagada%2C%20Odisha%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20are%20children%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ETijiraja%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20how%20can%20we%20allow%20our%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ETijmali%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20be%20mined%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETijmali%20is%20or%20soul%2C%20how%20can%20we%20live%20without%20our%20soul%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMining%20will%20destroy%20not%20just%20the%20streams%20but%20their%3B%20how%20can%20we%20allow%20that%20to%20happen%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20shall%20fight%20for%20our%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emali%20parbat%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eour%20forests%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eby%20all%20means%20available%2C%20but%20will%20not%20let%20Vedanta%20mine%20our%20soul.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdivasi%20and%20Dalit%20communities%20for%20generations%20have%20been%20custodians%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3ETijmali%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20abundant%20in%20rich%20bio-cultural%20diversity.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ETijmali%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20gets%20its%20name%20from%20the%20local%20legend%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ETijraja%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20whose%20abode%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ETijmali%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20who%20is%20worshipped%20as%20the%20supreme%20deity%20of%20the%20hills.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ETijmali%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20an%20example%20of%20the%20historical%20misappropriation%20of%20indigenous%20spatial%20categories%2C%20and%20its%20interrelation%20with%20their%20spiritual%20life-worlds.%20It%20is%20part%20of%20the%201%2C000%20sq%20km%20long%20southern%20stretch%20of%20the%20Eastern%20Ghats%20range%2C%20spreading%20over%20both%20Thuamul%20Rampur%20block%20of%20Kalahandi%20and%20Kashipur%20block%20of%20Rayagada%20districts%20in%20Odisha.%20Thuamul%20Rampur%20block%20in%20Kalahandi%20and%20Rayagada%20district%20in%20total%20are%20constitutionally%20designated%20Schedule%20V%20areas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15163147%2Funnamed-5.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15163147%2Funnamed-5.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15163147%2Funnamed-5-300x209.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684901%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22714%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPhoto%3A%20Rajaraman%20Sundaresan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20hill%20has%20several%20neighbouring%20mountain%20peaks%20like%20%3Cspan%3Elike%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ESasubaumali%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Batingmali%2C%20Majingmali%2C%20Kutrumali%20and%20Khandualmali.%20Each%20of%20these%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Emali%20(mountain)%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%20has%20rich%20socio-bio-cultural%20significance%20in%20the%20life-worlds%20of%20Indigenous%20populations%20who%20inhabit%20these%20regions.%20The%20Eco-Sensitive%20Zone%20(ESZ)%20of%20Karlapat%20Wildlife%20Sanctuary%2C%20known%20as%20a%20natural%20elephant%2C%20tiger%20and%20pangolin%20habitat%2C%20and%20adjacent%20to%20Khandualmali%20in%20Thuamul%20Rampur%20block%2C%20lies%20in%20close%20proximity%20to%20the%20proposed%20mining%20site%2C%20Tijmali%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0hills.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20March%201%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Vedanta%20Limited%20received%20a%20Letter%20of%20Intent%20from%20the%20Government%20of%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20Steel%20%26amp%3B%20Mines%20Department%20as%20the%20preferred%20bidder%20for%20bauxite%20mining%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ETijimali%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20over%20an%20area%20of%20over%201549.022%20hectares%20(equivalent%20to%20nearly%201880%20football%20fields).%20Vedanta%20has%20proposed%20to%20extract%209%20million%20tons%20per%20annum%20from%20the%20estimated%20bauxite%20reserve%20of%20311%20million%20tons.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20August%2014%2C%20the%20MoEFCC%20granted%20Vedanta%20a%20Terms%20of%20Reference%20(ToR)%20under%20the%20Environment%20Impact%20Assessment%20(EIA)%20Notification%2C%202006.%20Within%20a%20month%2C%20on%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20September%2013%2C%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20State%20Pollution%20Control%20Board%20(OSPCB)%20put%20up%20notices%20for%20conducting%20public%20hearings%20%E2%80%93%20a%20mandatory%20process%20for%20companies%20to%20obtain%20environmental%20clearance%20nods%20%E2%80%93%20in%20Rayagada%20and%20Kalahandi%20districts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%9CThe%20draft%20EIA%20report%20submitted%20by%20Vedanta%20as%20part%20of%20this%20mandatory%20process%2C%20has%20suppressed%20vital%20information%20about%20Tijmali%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0and%20the%20studies%20conducted%20for%20this%20report%20are%20based%20on%20erroneous%20claims.%20This%20gives%20Vedanta%20enough%20room%20to%20evade%20accountability%20and%20project%20itself%20as%20being%20committed%20to%20its%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.co.in%2Furl%3Fsa%3Dt%26rct%3Dj%26q%3D%26esrc%3Ds%26source%3Dweb%26cd%3D%26cad%3Drja%26uact%3D8%26ved%3D2ahUKEwijmJbcgLGCAxWSb2wGHasuAg0QFnoECAgQAw%26url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.vedantalimited.com%252Fuploads%252Finvestor-overview%252Fannual-report%252FExecutive-Summary-SR-FY23.pdf%26usg%3DAOvVaw1ASmfidn2befwBLe0yScLN%26opi%3D89978449%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eprincipal%20claim%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20mining%20%E2%80%98responsibly%E2%80%99%20(sic).%20This%20dubious%20claim%20has%20no%20precedence%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.co.in%2Furl%3Fsa%3Dt%26rct%3Dj%26q%3D%26esrc%3Ds%26source%3Dweb%26cd%3D%26cad%3Drja%26uact%3D8%26ved%3D2ahUKEwio9LaqgbGCAxV9amwGHU0NBTEQFnoECCYQAQ%26url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Ftheleaflet.in%252Fvedantas-serial-crimes-against-indian-people-land-and-water-expose-state-corporate-nexus-at-its-worst%252F%26usg%3DAOvVaw1EjTcmxIPEsUWZ2LvIM8_a%26opi%3D89978449%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehistory%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20wildlife%20biologist%20who%20studied%20Vedanta%E2%80%99s%20EIA%20report%20and%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20be%20named.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15163252%2Funnamed-6.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15163252%2Funnamed-6.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15163252%2Funnamed-6-300x186.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15163252%2Funnamed-6-1024x636.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684902%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22745%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPhoto%3A%20Rajaraman%20Sundaresan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20draft%20EIA%20shows%20that%20data%20gathering%20on%20various%20ecological%20elements%20was%20undertaken%20in%20the%20periods%20prior%20to%20the%20issuance%20of%20ToR%20which%20mandates%20that%20EIA%20studies%20must%20cover%20other%20periods%20of%20the%20year%20for%20proper%20assessment%20of%20a%20habitat%20and%20movement%20of%20wildlife%20across%20any%20mining%20lease%20area.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20biological%20study%20submitted%20as%20part%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fospcboard.org%2Fwp-content%2Fplugins%2Fhearing%2Fuploads%2Ffiles_1694775426_2127154790.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edraft%20EIA%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20clearly%20shows%20that%20the%20proposed%20area%20has%20been%20a%20rich%20habitat%20and%20a%20corridor%20for%20diverse%20wildlife%20species%2C%20particularly%20Schedule%20(I)%20under%20the%20Wildlife%20Protection%20Act%2C%201972.%20The%20draft%20EIA%20does%20not%20identify%20all%20the%20potential%20risks%20to%20the%20environment%20or%20expand%20the%20complexities%20of%20the%20impacts%20of%20its%20mining%20on%20not%20only%20the%20environment%20but%20also%20the%20people%20living%20in%20the%20region%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20biologist%20added.%20Contrary%20to%20claims%20made%20in%20the%20draft%20EIA%20of%20the%20proposed%20project%20affecting%2018%20villages%2C%20local%20people%20say%20it%20will%20affect%20more%20than%2050%20villages%20across%20the%20region.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20must%20be%20noted%20that%20since%20the%20mine%20lease%20area%20of%20Tijmali%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0falls%20across%20two%20administrative%20districts%20%E2%80%93%20Rayagada%20and%20Kalahandi%2C%20as%20per%20the%20EIA%20notification%2C%202006%20there%20must%20be%20separate%20public%20hearings%20for%20each%20district.%20Accordingly%2C%20the%20first%20public%20hearing%20was%20held%20on%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20October%2016%2C%202023%2C%20at%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3ESunger%20Panchayat%20of%20Kashipur%20block%20for%20Rayagada%2C%20and%20the%20second%20on%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0October%3C%2Fspan%3E%2018%2C%20%3Cspan%3E2023%20at%20Kerpai%20Panchayat%20of%20Thuamul%20Rampur%20block%20for%20Kalahandi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMore%20than%20a%20week%20before%20Vedanta%20received%20its%20ToR%2C%20its%20mine%20developing%20operator%20Mythri%20Infrastructure%20and%20Mining%20India%20sent%20its%20staff%20to%20visit%20project-affected%20villages%20to%20promise%20money%20and%20freebies%20to%20lure%20people%20to%20support%20the%20mining%20project%20in%20the%20upcoming%20public%20hearing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15163731%2Funnamed-9.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15163731%2Funnamed-9.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15163731%2Funnamed-9-300x210.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15163731%2Funnamed-9-1024x715.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684904%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22838%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPhoto%3A%20Rajaraman%20Sundaresan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EJuly%2030%2C%20about%20200%20women%2C%20youth%2C%20and%20men%20of%20several%20villages%20protested%20Vedanta%E2%80%99s%20mining%20project%20and%20confronted%20the%20Mythri%20officials%2C%20reprimanding%20them%20for%20venturing%20into%20their%20villages%20without%20the%20Gram%20Sabha%E2%80%99s%20approval.%20Following%20this%2C%20on%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20August%204%2C%20hundreds%20of%20people%20gathered%20at%20Lakris%20village%20and%20confronted%20the%20company%20officials%20once%20again%20for%20trying%20to%20bribe%20villagers%20into%20consenting%20to%20Vedanta%E2%80%99s%20mining%20project.%20Despite%20this%2C%20the%20company%20officials%20made%20several%20attempts%20to%20venture%20into%20the%20villages%20and%20go%20up%20to%20Tijmali%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0hilltop.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20alleged%20by%20several%20villagers%20that%20Mythri%20officials%20were%20involved%20in%20collecting%20bank%20account%20and%20Aadhar%20card%20details%20of%20people%20with%20the%20promise%20that%20they%20would%20deposit%20Rs%201%2C500%20in%20return%20for%20their%20support%20of%20the%20mining%20project.%20On%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20August%2012%2C%20during%20one%20such%20confrontation%2C%20the%20company%20agents%20were%20also%20made%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbehanbox.com%2F2023%2F11%2F03%2Fwhy-odishas-adivasi-women-are-trekking-forests-and-hills-to-collectivise-against-a-mining-project%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewrite%20a%20letter%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20assuring%20people%20that%20they%20would%20not%20enter%20the%20area%20without%20prior%20consent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20retaliation%2C%20Mythri%20officials%20registered%20five%20FIRs%20against%20villagers%20on%20different%20dates%20at%20Kashipur%20police%20station%20accusing%20about%2095%20persons%20of%20threatening%20and%20assaulting%20them%20with%20axes%2C%20%3Cem%3Elathis%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20taking%20them%20hostage.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20fallout%20of%20these%20FIRs%20was%20that%20from%20the%20night%20of%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20August%2013%2C%20as%20many%20as%2021%20people%20were%20arrested%20from%20six%20villages%20and%20sent%20to%20Rayagada%20Sub-jail.%20The%20remaining%20continue%20to%20face%20persecution%20as%20they%20are%20charged%20under%20several%20IPC%20sections%20like%20307%20and%20364%20which%20amounts%20to%20murder%20and%20rioting.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETijmali%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Edefenders%20live%20in%20a%20state%20of%20fear%20anticipating%20a%20police%20crackdown%20at%20any%20time%20due%20to%20the%20continuous%20police%20patrolling.%20Police%20and%20paramilitary%20checkpoints%20at%20road%20junctures%20and%20village%20entry%20points%20continued%20till%20the%20recent%20public%20hearings.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15163814%2Funnamed-8.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15163814%2Funnamed-8.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15163814%2Funnamed-8-300x188.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15163814%2Funnamed-8-1024x641.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684905%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22751%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPolice%20check%20posts%20set%20up%20on%20the%20route%20to%20public%20hearings.%20Photo%3A%20Rajaraman%20Sundaresan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESeveral%20women%20have%20arrived%20from%20Tijmali%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0hilltop%20after%20spending%20hours%20collecting%20s%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eiali%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(bauhinia%20vahlii)%20leaves.%20One%20of%20the%20women%2C%20a%2052-year-old%20Adivasi%20elder%2C%20not%20wanting%20to%20be%20named%2C%20explained%2C%20%E2%80%9CWomen%20know%20what%20Tijmali%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20means%20to%20us.%20There%20are%20more%20than%2050%20caves%20in%20Tijmali%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20like%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EBagpar%2C%20Gumedapar%2C%20Ranipar%2C%20Jitajharanpar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Epar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20refers%20to%20cave)%20which%20are%20sacred%20to%20us.%20We%20conduct%20rituals%20during%20different%20seasons%20in%20these%20caves.%20Wouldn%E2%80%99t%20mining%20destroy%20these%20caves%3F%20Besides%2C%20Tijmali%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0is%20the%20main%20source%20of%20water%20for%20us.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EPanichida%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20or%20as%20some%20call%20it%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ESwadhgad%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20the%20hilltop%20is%20one%20the%20main%20sources%20of%20water%20to%20several%20streams%20that%20flow%20to%20our%20farms%20and%20villages%20feeds.%20Mining%20will%20destroy%20these%20200-odd%20streams%20and%20their%20sources.%20How%20will%20we%2C%20the%20trees%20and%20animals%20survive%20then%3F%20We%20go%20to%20the%20hilltop%20to%20collect%20s%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eiali%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20leaves%2C%20honey%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Egooseberry%2C%20tamarind%2C%20guava%2C%20%3Cem%3Ej%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3Eamun%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(java%20plum)%2C%20%3Cem%3Ej%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3Ehuna%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(resins)%20and%20%3Cem%3Ep%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3Ehul%3C%2Fem%3E%20jhadu%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(hill%20broom).%20All%20these%20have%20medicinal%20values%20and%20we%20sell%20them%20for%20our%20livelihood%20too.%20Will%20these%20remain%20if%20mining%20happens%20in%20Tijmali%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EManjula%20Nayak%2C%20a%2024-year-old%20Dalit%20farmer%20from%20Banteji%2C%20has%20two%20children%20and%20is%20determined%20to%20save%20the%20hills%20from%20mining.%20Her%20partner%2C%20Kartika%20Nayak%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9Cvehemently%20opposes%20the%20mining%20of%20the%20hills%20and%20that%20is%20why%20the%20police%20is%20targeting%20him.%20Because%20of%20the%20frequent%20midnight%20raids%2C%20youth%20and%20elders%20from%20our%20village%20are%20hiding%20in%20the%20forests.%20Life%20has%20become%20miserable%20for%20us%20since%20Vedanta%3Cspan%3E-Mythri%3C%2Fspan%3E%20arrived%20here.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15164050%2Funnamed-10.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15164050%2Funnamed-10.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15164050%2Funnamed-10-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15164050%2Funnamed-10-1024x577.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684906%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22676%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPhoto%3A%20Rajaraman%20Sundaresan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERanidei%20Majhi%2C%20a%2045-year-old%20Kandha%20Adivasi%20farmer%20from%20Banteji%2C%20speaking%20about%20her%20community%E2%80%99s%20relationship%20with%20Tijmali%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20grow%20%3Cem%3Em%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3Eandia%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(finger%20millets)%2C%20%3Cem%3Ek%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3Eosala%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(little%20millets)%2C%20%3Cem%3Ek%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eangu%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(foxtail%20millets)%2C%20%3Cem%3Ej%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ehudung%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(long%20beans)%20and%20%3Cem%3Eb%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eiri%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(black%20gram)%20in%20the%20mountains.%20We%20collect%20about%2015-20%20varieties%20of%20tubers%20like%20%3Cem%3Es%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eemilikanda%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(casava)%2C%20