fluence%2C%20concentrating%20on%20curriculum%2C%20teaching%20methods%2C%20and%20evaluations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20in%20partnership%20with%20state%20governments%2C%20the%20organisation%20is%20introducing%20new%20curriculums%20such%20as%20the%20Happiness%20Curriculum%20in%20Delhi%2C%20Anandam%20Pattacharya%20in%20Uttarakhand%2C%20a%20whole-child%20development%20pedagogical%20approach%20in%20Jharkhand%20and%20a%20Life%20Skills%20Curriculum%20in%20Nagaland%20and%20Telangana.%20The%20organisation%20also%20support%20the%20state%20education%20departments%20with%20new%20pedagogical%20approaches%2C%20teacher%20training%20and%20introducing%20new%20assessment%20frameworks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%98Building%20the%20Field%E2%80%99%20strategic%20approach%20is%20working%20to%20enable%20a%20mindset%20shift%20among%20diverse%20stakeholders%20in%20the%20learning%20ecosystem%20to%20bring%20in%20a%20collaborative%20approach%20to%20education%2C%20encompassing%20the%20broader%20community%2C%20decision%20makers%2C%20professionals%20in%20various%20fields%2C%20parents%2C%20teachers%20and%20other%20stakeholders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20organisation%20intends%20to%20maximise%20impact%20through%20large-scale%20dissemination%20of%20real%20world%20research%20findings%2C%20engage%20in%20critical%20dialogues%20to%20listen%20to%20diverse%20narratives%20of%20success%2C%20amplify%20young%20people%E2%80%99s%20voices%20through%20collaborations%20and%20advocate%20for%20thriving%20as%20the%20purpose%20of%20education%20by%20weaving%20together%20people%2C%20places%20and%20voices%20supported%20by%20high%20impact%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESpearheading%20change%20through%20sports%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDream%20a%20Dream%20works%20with%20both%20affordable%20private%20schools%20and%20State%20Governments.%20For%20instance%2C%20they%20partnered%20with%20the%20Delhi%20government%20and%20other%20nonprofit%20organisations%20to%20implemen