nt%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F29150739%2FScreenshot-2023-05-29-at-3.07.06-PM.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Even%20as%20the%20country%20celebrated%20the%20festival%20of%20lights%2C%20the%20darkness%20in%20faraway%20Manipur%20turned%20a%20deeper%20shade%20of%20black.%20This%20Diwali%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20(MHA)%20proscribed%20eight%20armed%20groups%20hailing%20from%20the%20north-eastern%20state.%20The%20MHA%20stated%20in%20its%20press%20note%20that%20they%20belong%20to%20the%20Meitei%20community%2C%20an%20unusual%20mention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKham%20Khan%20Suan%20Hausing%2C%20academic%20and%20a%20prominent%20voice%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20%C2%A0minority%20Kuki%20community%20which%20has%20been%20locked%20in%20bitter%20ethnic%20conflict%20with%20the%20majority%20Meiteis%20since%20May%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fkksuanh%2Fstatus%2F1724113002075496639%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Esaid%20this%20underlined%3C%2Fa%3E%20an%20%E2%80%9Cinteresting%20turnaround%20in%20Government%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20stand%20on%20who%20pose(s)%20real%20threats%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20national%20security.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20asked%2C%20%E2%80%9CApparently%2C%20event%20management%20sits%20uneasily%20with%20ground%20realities.%20A%20wake-up%20call%20and%20time%20to%20re-impose%20AFSPA%20in%20%E2%80%98disturbed%E2%80%99%20Meitei-dominated%20valley%20areas%20of%20Manipur%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20sharper%20question%20to%20the%20central%20government%20could%20have%20been%20this%20though%3A%20Has%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20repeated%20claim%20to%20the%20media%20that%20%E2%80%98peace%20has%20come%E2%80%99%20to%20the%20Northeast%20due%20to%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%2C%20become%20a%20bottleneck%20for%20the%20MHA%3F%20Especially%2C%20as%20it%20is%20balking%20about%20considering%20the%20reintroduction%20of%20the%20controversial%20AFSPA%20(Armed%20Forces%20%E2%80%93%20Special%20Powers%20%E2%80%93%20Act)%20in%20Manipur%20where%20armed%20groups%20seemed%20to%20have%20played%20a%20considerable%20role%20in%20escalating%20the%20recent%20violence%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Double%20engine%E2%80%99%20power%20takes%20a%20hit%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20say%2C%20scenes%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20security%20forces%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fmanipur%2F48-hour-manipur-bandh-from-midnight-to-demand-release-of-five-arrested-youths-2691398%5C%22%3Ehaving%20to%20let%20go%20cadres%20of%20a%20banned%20outfit%20in%20the%20Northeast%3C%2Fa%3E%20accused%20of%20attacks%20because%20of%20pressure%20from%20a%20%E2%80%98mob%E2%80%99%20have%20been%20unprecedented%20and%20have%20greatly%20damaged%20the%20%E2%80%98double-engine%E2%80%99%20government%E2%80%99s%20credibility%2C%20both%20in%20Delhi%20and%20Imphal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENever%20have%20we%20seen%20so%20many%20armed%20groups%20declared%20banned%20(for%20as%20many%20as%20a%20decade)%20anywhere%20in%20the%20Northeast%20without%20the%20Centre%20switching%20on%20the%20%E2%80%98disturbed%20area%E2%80%99%20button%20in%20AFSPA%20to%20grant%20extra%20powers%20for%20the%20security%20forces%20to%20hunt%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20when%20these%20same%20outfits%20were%20banned%20by%20MHA%20for%20five%20years%20(this%20recent%20ban%20is%20a%20renewal%20of%20sorts%20that%20way)%2C%20AFSPA%20was%20functional%20across%20Manipur%20except%20in%20the%20Imphal%20municipality%20area.%20Even%20when%20the%20ban%20on%20these%20outfits%20continued%2C%20the%20MHA%2C%20in%202022%2C%20made%20a%20rare%20move%20by%20removing%20the%20%E2%80%98disturbed%20area%E2%80%99%20tag%20from%2015%20police%20stations%20spread%20across%20the%20Meitei-dominated%20valley%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%2026%2C%20barely%20a%20few%20weeks%20before%20this%20May%203%20violence%20gripped%20Manipur%2C%20four%20more%20police%20stations%20of%20the%20valley%20districts%20were%20dropped%20from%20the%20ambit%20of%20AFSPA%20by%20the%20MHA.%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20was%20heard%20telling%20local%20media%20in%20Imphal%20then%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20historic%20moment%20was%20achieved%2C%20following%20the%20era%20of%20peace%20and%20prosperity%20that%20came%20in%20the%20state%20with%20the%20arrival%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi-led%20BJP%20government%20in%20Manipur.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Buck%20Stops%20at%20the%20Centre%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20even%20sharper%20question%20would%20then%20be%20%E2%80%93%20Has%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%E2%80%99s%20claim%20that%20Modi%2C%20or%20more%20specifically%2C%20the%20national%20security%20adviser%20(NSA)%20Ajit%20Doval%E2%80%99s%20assessment%20of%20%E2%80%98peace%20has%20come%E2%80%99%20in%20Manipur%20gone%20horribly%20wrong%3F%20Was%20that%20claim%20of%20the%20government%20of%20the%20day%20mere%20hogwash%2C%20a%20claim%20without%20any%20basis%2C%20then%3F%20Was%20it%20a%20miscalculation%2C%20misinterpretation%20of%20the%20ground%20reality%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20Peace%20in%20Manipur%20to%20Date%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20questions%20are%20applicable%20because%2C%20if%20%E2%80%98peace%E2%80%99%20in%20that%20border%20state%20was%20%E2%80%98in%20existence%E2%80%99%20only%20till%20this%20March%20end%2C%20as%20per%20the%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20assessment%2C%20how%20was%20it%20that%20only%20in%20the%20first%20week%20of%20May%20all%20hell%20broke%20loose%2C%20and%20a%20band%20of%20proscribed%20%E2%80%98Meitei%E2%80%99%20armed%20groups%20got%20down%20to%20action%20in%20an%20area%2C%20given%20the%20green%20signal%20for%20removal%20of%20AFSPA%3F%20The%20common%20refrain%20in%20Imphal%20is%2C%20these%20outfits%20might%20have%20been%20instrumental%20in%20looting%20dozens%20of%20those%20AFSPA-free%20police%20stations%20for%20arms%20and%20ammunition.%20Pertinent%20as%20they%20may%20be%2C%20but%20the%20dilemma%20before%20the%20independent%20media%20is%2C%20whom%20should%20it%20pose%20these%20questions%3F%20Who%20is%20responsible%20for%20it%3F%20Imphal%20or%20New%20Delhi%3F%20Will%20there%20even%20be%20a%20reply%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20MHA%20press%20note%20accused%20these%20outfits%20of%20%E2%80%9Cmobilising%20cadres%20for%20escalating%20their%20secessionist%2C%20subversive%2C%20terrorist%20and%20violent%20activities%3B%20propagate%20anti-national%20activities%20in%20collusion%20with%20forces%20inimical%20to%20sovereignty%20and%20integrity%20of%20India%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20NSA%20is%20so%20far%20conspicuously%20quiet%20on%20Manipur%2C%20let%20alone%20seen%20repeating%20his%20%E2%80%98biryani%E2%80%99%20moment%20to%20symbolise%20%E2%80%98peace%20has%20come%E2%80%99%20to%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMore%20Questions%20Need%20to%20be%20Asked%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENevertheless%2C%20questions%20must%20be%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20here%20is%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHas%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20(it%20has%20the%20double%20engine%20variety%20in%20Manipur)%20decided%20to%20not%20bring%20back%20AFSPA%20in%20the%20valley%20areas%20of%20Manipur%20for%20now%20because%20it%20is%20a%20sensitive%20subject%20for%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20majority%20community%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20one-of-a-kind%20fast%20by%20Irom%20Sharmila%20was%20a%20non-violent%20rebellion%20against%20New%20Delhi%20for%20clamping%20down%20the%20draconian%20law%20largely%20on%20the%20Meitei%20community.%20The%20memories%20of%20rapes%2C%20killings%20and%20encounters%20by%20security%20forces%20are%20still%20fresh%20in%20the%20streets%20of%20Imphal.%20No%20one%20in%20the%20valley%20wants%20to%20return%20to%20those%20dark%20days.%20No%20affected%20family%20has%20got%20justice%20yet.%20All%20Manipuris%20want%20to%20see%20better%20days%2C%20not%20naked%20display%20of%20arms%20that%20make%20life%20so%20cheap%20which%20occurred%20recently.%20With%20so%20many%20dead%20and%20thousands%20turning%20homeless%2C%20many%20feel%20that%20the%20state%20clearly%20failed%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20that%20elections%20recur%20every%20five%20years%20is%20also%20a%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20is%20it%20then%20important%20to%20ask%20if%20the%20present%20decision%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%20to%20not%20reimpose%20AFSPA%20in%20the%20valley%20areas%20of%20Manipur%20in%20spite%20of%20MHA%20finding%20that%20secessionist%20armed%20groups%20have%20gained%20ground%20(and%20muscle)%20have%20to%20do%20more%20with%20voter%20sentiment%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnalysis%20says%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20been%20careful%20about%20timing%20policy%20decisions%20and%20their%20announcement%2C%20keeping%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20electoral%20prospects%20in%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20BJP%20could%20win%20a%20clear%20majority%20in%20the%20Manipur%20assembly%20for%20the%20first%20time%20due%20to%20the%20overwhelming%20support%20to%20the%20party%20by%20the%20Meitei%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20Modi%20the%20campaigner%20went%20to%20Imphal%20to%20seek%20votes%20in%202022%20but%20Modi%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20didn%E2%80%99t%2C%20or%20couldn%E2%80%99t%2C%20when%20their%20lives%20were%20turning%20upside%20down%20is%20a%20grouse%20most%20Meiteis%20nurse%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20continuing%20post%20May%203%20violence%20and%20disruption%20in%20the%20state.%20Only%20time%20will%20answer%20conclusively%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20then%20a%20palliative%20by%20an%20election-centric%20ruling%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EElectoral%20gambits%20and%20Myanmar%20unrest%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20just%20in%20Manipur%2C%20but%20across%20the%20Northeast%2C%20it%20is%20an%20%E2%80%98open%20secret%E2%80%99%20that%20several%20political%20leaders%20of%20all%20shades%20covertly%20misuse%20insurgents%20who%20are%20engaged%20in%20peace%20talks%20with%20the%20central%20and%20state%20governments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20militants%20are%20overground%20because%20of%20the%20sustained%20ceasefire%20agreements%20with%20the%20government.%20Anyway%2C%20the%20past%20of%20several%20top%20political%20leaders%20from%20across%20the%20region%20are%20linked%20to%20banned%20armed%20outfits%20is%20no%20secret.%20Manipur%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%2C%20too%2C%20was%20once%20charged%20under%20the%20National%20Security%20Act%20(NSA)%20for%20allegedly%20supporting%20the%20People%E2%80%99s%20Liberation%20Army%20of%20Manipur%20(PLA)%2C%20one%20of%20the%20groups%20banned%20by%20MHA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20with%20things%20taking%20a%20sharp%20and%20surprising%20turn%20in%20neighbouring%20Myanmar%2C%20such%20election-time%20misuse%20of%20armed%20groups%20in%20Manipur%20cannot%20be%20taken%20lightly.%20The%20MHA%20renewing%20the%20ban%20on%20so%20many%20insurgent%20groups%2C%20even%20if%20they%20are%20not%20large%20in%20cadre%20strength%2C%20also%20gains%20more%20significance%20considering%20their%20bases%20are%20typically%20across%20the%20international%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20joint%20offensive%20carried%20out%20by%20Myanmar%E2%80%99s%20pro-democracy%20forces%20along%20with%20local%20armed%20groups%20in%20Chin%20and%20Sagaing%20regions%20since%20this%20October-end%20has%20succeeded%20in%20snatching%20away%20from%20the%20Myanmar%20ruling%20Junta%2C%20strips%20of%20strategic%20areas%20along%20the%20Indian%20border.%20These%20land%20strips%20are%20not%20just%20adjacent%20to%20Mizoram%20but%20some%20are%20close%20to%20Manipur%2C%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Nagaland%2C%20too.%20In%20the%20larger%20scope%20of%20developments%20in%20that%20country%2C%20a%20key%20trade%20route%20with%20China%20in%20the%20Shan%20state%20has%20also%20fallen%20into%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98rebels%E2%80%99.%20These%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fmyanmar-rebel-forces-capture-key-trade-routes-with-china%5C%22%3Econtinuous%20%E2%80%98wins%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20coming%20at%20a%20time%20when%20Myanmar%E2%80%99s%20government-in-exile%2C%20a%20supporter%20of%20this%20offensive%2C%20is%20noting%20that%20India%20is%20engaging%20only%20with%20the%20Junta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MHA%20in%20its%20wisdom%20has%20not%20lifted%20AFSPA%20from%20areas%20of%20Manipur%20that%20border%20Myanmar%3B%20even%20though%20in%20that%20stretch%20all%20the%20armed%20groups%20are%20under%20ceasefire%20and%20in%20peace%20talks%20with%20the%20Indian%20government%2C%20unlike%20the%20Meitei%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShifting%20Blame%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPost%20May%203%20violence%2C%20both%20the%20state%20chief%20minister%20and%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%20had%20blamed%20%E2%80%98Myanmar%E2%80%99%20(indicating%20drug%20lords%20and%20illegal%20immigrants%20from%20the%20country)%20for%20it.%20This%2C%20then%20makes%20Hausing%E2%80%99s%20comments%20cited%20above%20more%20relevant.%20The%20MHA%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20ban%20these%20Meitei%20groups%20seemingly%20operating%20deep%20inside%20Manipur%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffrontline.thehindu.com%2Fthe-nation%2Fcentre-blaming-myanmar-migrants-for-manipur-violence-is-dangerous%2Farticle67212603.ece%5C%22%3Ecame%20just%20weeks%20after%20%E2%80%98external%20forces%E2%80%99%20were%20solely%20blamed%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20internal%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHas%20the%20BJP%20government%E2%80%99s%20narrative%20on%20those%20responsible%20for%20Manipur%20violence%20then%2C%20again%20shifted%20significantly%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700055004000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F29150739%2FScreenshot-2023-05-29-at-3.07.06-PM.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fbanning-nine-meitei-groups-signals-many-shifts-in-and-around-manipur%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20is%20much%20to%20be%20read%20in%20how%20t