ia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fasha-san-3-1699623083-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334031%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAsha%20(second%20from%20the%20right%20in%20the%20last%20row)%20with%20her%20family%20and%20neighbours%20in%20Japan.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20not%20easy%20to%20communicate%20with%20each%20other%20then.%20They%20used%20to%20write%20messages%20on%20very%20thin%20rice%20papers%2C%20stitch%20them%20into%20blankets%2C%20and%20with%20the%20help%20of%20shipmen%2C%20it%20would%20be%20sent%20to%20Netaji%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tanvi%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20her%20parents%20remained%20dedicated%20to%20the%20freedom%20movement%2C%20Asha%20continued%20her%20schooling%20in%20Showa%20University%20at%20Tokyo.%20She%20discontinued%20her%20education%20after%20joining%20the%20Rani%20Jhansi%20regiment%20at%20the%20age%20of%2017.%20From%20Tokyo%2C%20she%20went%20to%20the%20training%20camp%20in%20Bangkok%20without%20any%20proper%20channels%20of%20transport%20due%20to%20the%20ongoing%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20language%20being%20a%20barrier%20as%20Asha%20grew%20up%20speaking%20Japanese%2C%20she%20made%20friends%20at%20the%20regiment.%20The%20story%20becomes%20humorous%20and%20thrilling%20when%20she%20writes%20about%20learning%20Hindi%20and%20firing%20a%20machine%20gun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20book%2C%20she%20writes%2C%20%E2%80%9CTo%20be%20honest%2C%20anything%2C%20including%20a%20bomb%20falling%20on%20my%20head%20will%20be%20easier%20than%20learning%20how%20to%20write%20Hindi.%E2%80%9D%20In%20fact%20when%20she%20was%20offered%20%3Cem%3Emakki%20ki%20roti%20%3C%2Fem%3Eby%20an%20Indian%20family%2C%20she%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20%3Cem%3Echapati%20%3C%2Fem%3E(flatbread)%20made%20of%20flies!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETanvi%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20Bangkok%2C%20she%20was%20trained%20to%20use%20machine%20guns%2C%20how%20to%20hold%20and%20fire%20pistols%20at%20the%20enemy%2C%20learn%20the%20tactics%20of%20guerilla%20warfare%2C%20and%20how%20to%20drive%20a%20truck.%20She%20discovered%20what%20it%20means%20to%20be%20a%20patriot%20fighting%20for%20the%20liberation%20of%20a%20country%20she%20has%20no%20memories%20of%20but%20carries%20deep%20in%20her%20heart.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fasha-san-1-1699622951.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%201945%2C%20Asha%20became%20a%20lieutenant%20of%20the%20Rani%20of%20Jhansi%20Regiment%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Army.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fasha-san-1-1699622951.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fasha-san-1-1699622951-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fasha-san-1-1699622951-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fasha-san-1-1699622951-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fasha-san-1-1699622951-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334027%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%201945%2C%20Asha%20became%20a%20lieutenant%20of%20the%20Rani%20of%20Jhansi%20Regiment%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Army.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EKadam%20Kadam%20Badhaye%20Ja%20%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20her%20training%2C%20Asha%2C%20along%20with%20her%20regiment%2C%20set%20out%20on%20foot%20to%20march%20from%20Bangkok%20to%20the%20far%20off%20Burma%20(present-day%20Myanmar)%20in%201945.%20Amid%20bombings%2C%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20armed%20force%20remained%20adamant%20as%20they%20sang%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EKadam%20Kadam%20Badhaye%20Ja%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%93%20the%20regimental%20quick%20march%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Army.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20regiment%20managed%20to%20reach%20the%20banks%20of%20the%20Irrawaddy%20River%20%E2%80%94%20Myanmar%E2%80%99s%20largest%20river%20and%20most%20important%20commercial%20waterway%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20flooded.%20This%20made%20it%20impossible%20for%20them%20to%20cross%20the%20river%20and%20join%20the%20major%20INA%20army%20on%20the%20other%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20the%20regiment%20set%20their%20camps%20on%20the%20bank.%20However%2C%20they%20were%20attacked%20by%20the%20British%20and%20put%20behind%20bars%20for%20over%20a%20month.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20were%20forced%20to%20retreat%20to%20Bangkok.%20While%20all%20the%20other%20women%20went%20back%20to%20their%20homes%2C%20%3Cem%3Edadi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(grandma)%20had%20nowhere%20to%20go.%20At%20that%20point%2C%20her%20father%2C%20who%20was%20out%20on%20a%20secret%20mission%2C%20was%20put%20in%20a%20Singapore%20jail.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20news%20of%20the%20atomic%20bombings%20in%20Japan%20surfaced%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20August%201945%2C%20Hiroshima%20and%20Nagasaki%20were%20bombed%20with%20nuclear%20weapons%20and%20the%20Japanese%20forces%20were%20forced%20to%20surrender.%20Two%20weeks%20later%2C%20on%2018%20August%201945%2C%20the%20plane%20carrying%20Netaji%2C%20who%20was%20on%20his%20way%20to%20Tokyo%2C%20crashed.%20This%20came%20as%20a%20defeat%20for%20the%20Indian%20National%20Army.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fasha-san-5-1699625115.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Asha%20h