ducation%20and%20got%20married%20in%201949.%20While%20she%20engaged%20herself%20in%20volunteer%20works%2C%20her%20contribution%2C%20like%20many%20other%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F190053%2Fgulab-kaur-woman-freedom-fighter-punjab-independence-day-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewomen%20freedom%20fighters%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Tanvi%20believes%2C%20remained%20unknown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F129013%2Fnetaji-subas-chandra-bose-death-conspiracies%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENetaji%E2%80%99s%20death%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20most%20of%20the%20records%20were%20destroyed.%20So%2C%20not%20many%20know%20the%20contribution%20of%20the%20INA%20and%20this%20young%20girl%20in%20the%20Indian%20freedom%20movement%20in%20East%20Asia.%20It%20was%20only%20after%20INA%20members%20came%20to%20India%20that%20Indian%20citizens%20got%20to%20know%20about%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20regiment%20in%20Japan%20and%20how%20these%20women%20fought%20for%20freedom.%20We%20only%20know%20about%20a%20handful%20of%20female%20freedom%20fighters%20despite%20them%20being%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20the%20freedom%20struggle%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20read%20such%20personal%20stories%20of%20war%2C%20it%20makes%20you%20understand%20what%20people%20went%20through%20and%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20take%20a%20country%2C%20that%20was%20nurtured%20by%20the%20sacrifices%20of%20people%2C%20for%20granted.%20Her%20story%20is%20inspirational%20for%20young%20women.%20For%20%3Cem%3Edadi%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Eit%20was%20only%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years%20that%20people%20started%20giving%20her%20recognition.%20This%20book%20has%20gotten%20some%20attention%20to%20her%20story%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Tanvi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20even%20went%20the%20extra%20mile%20to%20collate%20various%20ph