0other%20version%20of%20the%20sweet%E2%80%99s%20history%2C%20we%20travel%20to%20the%2017th-century%20Mughal%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20symbol%20of%20freedom%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20goes%20that%20around%201619%2C%20Emperor%20Jehangir%2C%20a%20prominent%20ruler%20of%20the%20Mughal%20dynasty%2C%20had%20captured%20Sikh%20gurus%2C%20holding%20them%20captive%20in%20the%20Gwalior%20Fort.%20It%20is%20said%20that%20Muslim%20orthodoxy%20made%20the%20emperor%20perceive%20Sikhs%20as%20a%20potential%20threat%20to%20the%20empire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20detainees%20at%20the%20time%20was%20the%20sixth%20Sikh%20Guru%2C%20Guru%20Hargovind.%20While%20held%20in%20captivity%2C%20the%20guru%20would%20frequently%20share%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333532%2Fpadma-shri-t-s-satyan-father-of-indian-photojournalism-mysuru-bengaluru-history-pictures%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehis%20teachings%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20the%20other%20inmates%2C%20attempting%20to%20make%20their%20time%20more%20bearable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWatching%20this%2C%20Emperor%20Jehangir%20came%20up%20with%20an%20unusual%20condition.%20The%20guru%20would%20be%20released%20and%20anyone%20who%20could%20cling%20to%20his%20robe%20would%20as%20he%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20fort%20be%20set%20free%20too.%20Intent%20on%20liberating%20everyone%2C%20the%20guru%20devised%20a%20way%20around%20this%20condition.%20He%20ordered%20the%2052%20monarchs%20to%20make%20a%20robe%20long%20enough%20to%20be%20worn%20by%20everyone%20in%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333570%2Fsachin-nag-won-only-gold-medal-swimming-for-india-at-asian-games-sports-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20set%20day%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20guru%20walked%20out%20of%20prison%20with%20everyone%20holding%20onto%20